to%20of%20food%20writer%20Suzy%20Karadsheh.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F659c41116979d73718215db5%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221095%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3ESuzy%20Karadsheh%2C%20author%20of%20the%20popular%20Mediterranean%20dish%20food%20blog%20and%20cookbook%2C%20said%20she%20grew%20up%20eating%20simple%2C%20delicious%20food%20that%20can%20also%20help%20with%20weight%20loss.%3Cp%3EAli%20Redmond%2FCaitlin%20Bensel%2FThe%20Mediterranean%20Dish%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cul%3E%3Cli%3EThe%20Mediterranean%20diet%20makes%20it%20simple%20to%20eat%20deliciously%20and%20nutritiously%2C%20a%20cookbook%20author%20said.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3EThe%20diet%20focuses%20on%20whole%2C%20plant-based%20foods%2C%20and%20includes%20a%20lot%20of%20flavors%20and%20variety.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3EIts%20focus%20on%20enjoyment%20and%20healthy%20habits%20can%20aid%20weight%20loss%20by%20helping%20you%20feel%20less%20deprived.%C2%A0%3C%2Fli%3E%3C%2Ful%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fmediterrean-diet-healthiest-best-overall-2024-1%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EMediterranean%20diet%3C%2Fa%3E%20isn't%20just%20the%20healthiest%20way%20to%20eat%20%E2%80%94%20it%20can%20also%20help%20you%20get%20more%20nutrients%20and%20even%20lose%20weight%20while%20enjoying%20simple%2C%20delicious%20food%2C%20according%20to%20a%20woman%20who's%20followed%20the%20diet%20her%20whole%20life.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ESuzy%20Karadsheh%2C%20founder%20of%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.themediterraneandish.com%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EMediterranean%20Dish%3C%2Fa%3E%20food%20blog%20and%20author%20of%20the%20best-selling%20cookbook%20of%20the%20same%20name%2C%20grew%20up%20in%20Egypt%2C%20in%20Port%20Said%20on%20the%20coast%20of%20the%20Mediterranean%20Sea.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EShe%20said%20Medittarnaean%20cuisines%20go%20far%20beyond%20the%20typical%20stereotype%20of%20Greek%20or%20Italian%20food%2C%20and%20share%20a%20common%20emphasis%20on%20simple%20but%20high-quality%20fresh%20ingredients%2C%20balanced%20nutrition%2C%20and%20compelling%20flavors.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAs%20a%20result%2C%20people%20often%20find%20that%20they%20can%20lose%20weight%20more%20easily%2C%20without%20feeling%20hungry%20or%20deprived%2C%20according%20to%20Karadsheh.%20Although%20not%20everyone%20will%20lose%20weight%20eating%20the%20Mediterranean%20way%2C%20she%20said%20she%20often%20hears%20from%20readers%20of%20her%20cookbook%20who%20shed%20pounds.%20She%20also%20said%20she%20lost%20weight%20over%20the%20recent%20holidays%20without%20cutting%20back%20on%20indulgence.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BSomething%20like%20weight%20loss%20becomes%20just%20a%20side%20effect%20of%20what%20you're%20already%20doing%20to%20be%20healthy%20rather%20than%20something%20you%20have%20to%20really%20push%20for%2C%26quot%3B%20Karadsheh%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%3EThe%20Mediterranean%20diet%20isn't%20restrictive%20and%20encourages%20you%20to%20enjoy%20eating%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EKaradsheh%20said%20a%20key%20part%20of%20the%20Mediterranean%20diet%20is%20an%20%26quot%3Babundance%20mindset%26quot%3B%20of%20looking%20forward%20to%20meals.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIt's%20so%20joyful%2C%26quot%3B%20she%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ERather%20than%20stipulating%20what%20you%20shouldn't%20eat%2C%20the%20Mediterranean%20diet%20focuses%20on%20what%20you%20can%20eat%2C%20and%20making%20it%20delicious.%20With%20this%20approach%2C%20you%20may%20find%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.insider.com%2Fhow-to-lose-weight-by-eating-more-according-to-dietitians-2023-4%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eyou%20fill%20up%20on%20nutrients%20and%20eat%20less%20junk%20food%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20such%20as%20processed%20foods%20or%20added%20sugars%2C%20dietitians%20previously%20told%20Business%20Insider.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20diet%20may%20also%20help%20you%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.insider.com%2F4-tips-for-sustainable-diets-that-arent-vegan-or-vegetarian-2022-9%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eeat%20more%20sustainably%3C%2Fa%3E.%20Karadsheh%20said%20she%20eats%20meat%2C%20eggs%2C%20and%20cheese%20regularly%2C%20but%20it's%20a%20small%20part%20of%20her%20overall%20diet.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%3E%3Cstrong%3EThe%20Mediterranean%20diet%20emphasizes%20simple%2C%20nutritious%20foods%20like%20olive%20oil%2C%20beans%2C%20and%20veggies%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EIt's%20a%20common%20misconception%20that%20cooking%20Mediterranean%20food%20will%20require%20you%20to%20import%20hard-to-find%20ingredients.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BMost%20of%20what%20we%20eat%20on%20the%20Mediterranean%20diet%20is%20available%20at%20your%20average%20grocery%20store%2C%26quot%3B%20Karadsheh%20said.%20%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EKaradsheh%20said%20staples%20in%20her%20kitchen%20include%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.insider.com%2F7-longevity-boosting-foods-blue-zones-add-to-shopping-list-2023-8%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%20cheap%2C%20accessible%2C%20and%20nutrient-dense%20foods%3C%2Fa%3E%20like%20beans%2C%20olive%20oil%2C%20grains%20including%20barley%20and%20rice%2C%20and%20seasonal%20vegetables.%20Many%20of%20these%20ingredients%20are%20rich%20in%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.insider.com%2Fguides%2Fhealth%2Fdiet-nutrition%2Ffiber-benefits%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Efiber%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20a%20nutrient%20that%20can%20aid%20weight%20loss%20by%20helping%20you%20feel%20more%20full%20after%20eating.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%3E%3Cstrong%3EMediterranean%20recipes%20are%20beginner-friendly%20and%20packed%20with%20flavor%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EMediterranean%20dishes%20are%20known%20for%20exciting%20and%20sometimes%20complex%20flavors%2C%20but%20it's%20easier%20than%20you%20think%20to%20make%20them%20at%20home%2C%20Karadsheh%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAn%20approachable%20way%20to%20start%20is%20by%20layering%20flavors%20with%20ingredients%20in%20your%20kitchen%2C%20she%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BCome%20at%20it%20from%20the%20perspective%20of%2C%20let%20me%20see%20if%20I%20can%20use%20what%20I%20have%2C%20the%20spices%20that%20I%20have%2C%20and%20then%20also%20consider%20the%20fresh%20ingredients%20that%20build%20flavor%20like%20citrus%2C%20garlic%2C%20onion%2C%26quot%3B%20she%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ECommon%20spices%20in%20Mediterranean%20cuisines%20from%20regions%20like%20Morroco%20and%20Egypt%20include%20cumin%2C%20coriander%2C%20paprika%2C%20turmeric%2C%20and%20cinnamon.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EFresh%20herbs%20such%20as%20mint%20and%20dill%2C%20aromatics%20like%20garlic%20and%20onions%2C%20and%20citrus%20juices%20round%20out%20the%20arsenal%20of%20flavor-building%20tools%20in%20a%20Mediterranean%20kitchen.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20simple%20recipes%20can%20make%20prepping%20healthy%20food%20more%20approachable%20even%20if%20you%20aren't%20an%20experienced%20home%20cook.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%3EMediterranean%20cuisine%20includes%20a%20huge%20variety%20so%20you%20won't%20get%20bored%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EOne%20major%20advantage%20of%20a%20Mediterranean%20diet%20is%20that%20it's%20easier%20to%20stick%20to%20because%20you%20don't%20have%20to%20worry%20about%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.insider.com%2Fcan-you-eat-same-thing-every-day-and-be-healthy-2020-11%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eeating%20the%20same%20foods%20every%20day%3C%2Fa%3E%20(if%20you%20don't%20want%20to).%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BA%20typical%20day%20of%20eating%20for%20me%20could%20be%20any%20number%20of%20flavors%2C%20which%20keeps%20it%20exciting%20for%20the%20family%2C%26quot%3B%20Karadsheh%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EA%20sample%20day%20of%20Mediterranean%20meals%20might%20include%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.themediterraneandish.com%2Fshakshuka-recipe%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eshakshuka%3C%2Fa%3E%20(a%20North%20African%20egg%20and%20tomato%20sauce%20dish)%20for%20breakfast%2C%20Turkish%20red%20lentil%20soup%20for%20lunch%2C%20and%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.th