%20in%20the%20dark%2C%26quot%3B%20on%20a%20NY%20street%2C%20she%20told%20jurors.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3E%26quot%3BIt's%20your%20choice%20in%20America%2C%26quot%3B%20she%20said%20of%20%26quot%3Bthe%20right%20to%20own%20a%20firearm%2C%26quot%3B%20prompting%20objections.%3C%2Fli%3E%3C%2Ful%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20case%20is%20about%20corruption%2C%20not%20gun%20rights%2C%20jurors%20in%20New%20York's%20NRA%20civil%20trial%20have%20been%20instructed%20by%20the%20judge%20%E2%80%94%20but%20that%20didn't%20stop%20a%20lawyer%20for%20the%20gun%20lobby%20from%20dropping%20some%20pretty%20blatant%20Second%20Amendment-rights%20propaganda%20into%20her%20opening%20statements%20Tuesday.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI%20never%20owned%20a%20gun%2C%26quot%3B%20NRA%20lawyer%20Sarah%20B.%20Rogers%20told%20six%20jurors%20and%20six%20alternates%20Tuesday%20in%20a%20Manhattan%20courtroom%2C%20as%20she%20neared%20the%20end%20of%20her%20openings.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI%20never%20thought%20I%20needed%20one%2C%26quot%3B%20she%20told%20them.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BAnd%20before%20working%20on%20this%20case%2C%20I%20didn't%20really%20agree%20with%20the%20NRA%20and%20the%20Second%20Amendment%2C%26quot%3B%20she%20said.%20%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThen%20one%20night%20walking%20home%2C%26quot%3B%20somewhere%20in%20New%20York%20City%2C%20she%20said%2C%20%26quot%3BI%20was%20attacked%20by%20two%20men%20in%20the%20dark.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAt%20this%20point%20%E2%80%94%20with%20the%20opening%20statement%20veering%20into%20personal%20opinion%20%E2%80%94%20Monica%20Connell%2C%20special%20counsel%20for%20the%20trial's%20plaintiffs%2C%20the%20New%20York%20attorney%20general's%20office%2C%20objected.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAttorney%20General%20Letitia%20James%20has%20sued%20the%20NRA%2C%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fthe-nra-is-not-wayne-lapierre-gun-lobby-tells-jury-2024-1%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eits%20outgoing%20longtime%20leader%20Wayne%20LaPierre%2C%3C%2Fa%3E%20and%20th