ook%20on%20the%20latter%20half%20of%20the%20nine-month%20world%20cruise.%20%3Cp%3EJeff%20Whyte%2FShutterstock%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EDespite%20cruise%20line%20President%20and%20CEO%20Michael%20Bayley's%20previous%20predictions%2C%20the%20world%20cruise%20has%20yet%20to%20sell%20out.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWhen%20it%20was%20first%20unveiled%2C%20the%20nine-month%20itinerary%20could%20be%20booked%20in%20four%20monthslong%20segments.%20The%20first%20is%20already%20underway.%20On%20Monday%2C%20a%20reservations%20representative%20told%20Business%20Insider%20that%20the%20second%20is%20now%20sold%20out.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBut%20the%20third%20and%20fourth%20segments%2C%20the%20%26quot%3BUltimate%20Middle%20East%20and%20Mediterranean%26quot%3B%20and%20%26quot%3BUltimate%20Europe%20and%20Beyond%26quot%3B%20itineraries%2C%20respectively%2C%20are%20still%20available%20to%20book.%20Both%20are%2063%20nights.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EA%20handful%20of%20the%20grand%20suites%2C%20interior%2C%20oceanview%2C%20and%20balcony%20cabins%20are%20available%20on%20the%20latter%20half%20of%20the%20itinerary%2C%20the%20representative%20said.%20The%20most%20expensive%20owner's%20suite%20is%20on%20the%20market%20as%20well.%20(Royal%20Caribbean%20did%20not%20respond%20to%20Business%20Insider's%20request%20to%20confirm%20this.)%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EStill%2C%20it%20won't%20be%20cheap%3A%20The%20least%20expensive%20interior%20stateroom%20starts%20at%20over%20%2416%2C850%20per%20person%20for%20the%20fourth%20segment%2C%20the%20representative%20told%20Business%20Insider.%20Broken%20down%2C%20it'll%20be%20almost%20%24270%20per%20day%20for%20a%20windowless%20cabin%2C%20a%20price%20comparable%20to%20nicer%20cabins%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Foceania-cruises-new-vista-ship-review-luxury-2023-10%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Epremium%20cruise%20ships%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIf%20several%20months%20at%20sea%20still%20seems%20too%20long%2C%20travelers%20can