C%20speaking%20to%20the%20media%20at%20his%20residence%20%60Matoshree'.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20affidavit%20before%20the%20SC%20was%20filed%20on%20Monday%2C%20the%20former%20CM%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMr%20Thackeray's%20ally%20and%20Nationalist%20Congress%20Party%20(NCP)%20founder%20Sharad%20Pawar%2C%20too%2C%20said%20that%20when%20someone%20who%20is%20hearing%20a%20case%20meets%20the%20person%20against%20whom%20the%20case%20is%20being%20heard%2C%20it%20%26quot%3Bleaves%20room%20for%20doubt%26quot%3B.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHitting%20back%2C%20Mr%20Narwekar%20said%20Mr%20Thackeray%20should%20know%20for%20what%20purposes%20a%20speaker%20could%20meet%20a%20chief%20minister.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIf%20he%20still%20levels%20such%20allegations%2C%20then%20his%20motive%20is%20very%20clear.%20There%20is%20no%20rule%20that%20a%20speaker%2C%20while%20hearing%20disqualification%20pleas%2C%20cannot%20do%20any%20other%20work%2C%26quot%3B%20Mr%20Narwekar%20contended.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20speaker%20met%20Mr%20Shinde%20at%20%60Varsha'%2C%20the%20chief%20minister's%20official%20residence%20in%20south%20Mumbai%20on%20Sunday.%20Mr%20Thackeray%20noted%20that%20the%20two%20had%20met%20in%20October%20last%20year%20too.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMr%20Narwekar's%20ruling%20will%20decide%20whether%20%26quot%3Bdemocracy%20exists%20in%20the%20country%20or%20not%26quot%3B%20or%20whether%20the%20two%20(speaker%20and%20chief%20minister)%20will%20%26quot%3Bmurder%26quot%3B%20democracy%2C%20said%20the%20Shiv%20Sena%20(UBT)%20leader.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWe%20have%20filed%20an%20affidavit%20asking%20whether%20there%20is%20collusion%20between%20the%20judge%20and%20the%20accused%2C%26quot%3B%20Thackeray%20said%2C%20asking%20whether%20there%20would%20be%20further%20delay%20by%20the%20speaker%20in%20giving%20the%20ruling.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMr%20Thackeray%2C%20who%20stepped%20down%20as%20CM%20in%20June-end%202022%20following%20the%20split%20in%20the%20Shiv%20Sena%2C%20a%20party%20founded%20by%20his%20father%20late%20Bal%20Thackeray%20in%201966%2C%20maintained%20the%20speaker%20never%20goes%20to%20meet%20the%20chief%20minister.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIt%20is%20the%20speaker%20who%20summons%20the%20latter%2C%20the%20former%20CM%20remarked.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Supreme%20Court%20last%20month%20extended%20the%20deadline%20to%20January%2010%20for%20Narwekar%20to%20decide%20on%20the%20cross-petitions%20filed%20by%20rival%20factions%20of%20the%20Shiv%20Sena%20seeking%20disqualification%20of%20each%20other's%20MLAs.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThackeray%20said%20since%20the%20SC%20directed%20Narwekar%20in%20May%20last%20year%20to%20take%20a%20decision%20on%20the%20disqualification%20pleas%2C%20the%20speaker%20has%20met%20the%20chief%20minister%20twice.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EShiv%20Sena%20(UBT)%20leader%20Anil%20Parab%20said%20such%20meetings%20must%20be%20brought%20to%20the%20Supreme%20Court's%20notice%20as%20it%20was%20a%20serious%20issue.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWe%20hope%20the%20apex%20court%20takes%20this%20matter%20seriously%2C%26quot%3B%20Parab%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EDeputy%20Chief%20Minister%20Devendra%20Fadnavis%20expressed%20confidence%20about%20the%20Shiv%20Sena-BJP-NCP%20(Ajit%20Pawar%20group)%20government%20remaining%20stable%20going%20forward%20The%20senior%20BJP%20leader%20stressed%20that%20the%20alliance%20government%20is%20%26quot%3Blegal%26quot%3B%20and%20hoped%20the%20speaker's%20ruling%20will%20give%20justice%20to%20them.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20speaker%20will%20take%20a%20proper%20and%20legal%20decision.%20Our%20side%20is%20strong.%20The%20government%20formed%20by%20us%20(BJP%20and%20Shiv%20Sena%20led%20by%20Shinde)%20is%20legally%20strong.%20We%20expect%20to%20get%20justice%20from%20the%20speaker....Our%20government%20was%20stable%20yesterday%20and%20it%20will%20remain%20stable%20tomorrow%20as%20well%2C%26quot%3B%20Fadnavis%20told%20reporters%20in%20Nagpur.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20June%202022%2C%20Shinde%20and%20several%20MLAs%20rebelled%20against%20the%20then-chief%20minister%20Thackeray%2C%20leading%20to%20a%20split%20in%20the%20Shiv%20Sena%20and%20fall%20of%20the%20Maha%20Vikas%20Aghadi%2C%20which%20also%20comprised%20the%20NCP%20and%20the%20Congress.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ECross-petitions%20were%20filed%20by%20the%20Shinde%20and%20Thackeray%20factions%20before%20the%20speaker%20seeking%20action%20against%20each%20other%20under%20anti-defection%20laws.%20The%20apex%20court%20in%20May%20last%20year%20had%20directed%20Mr%20Narwekar%20to%20adjudicate%20on%20the%20pleas%20expeditiously.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Election%20Commission%20had%20given%20the%20'Shiv%20Sena'%20name%20and%20'bow%20and%20arrow'%20symbol%20to%20the%20Shinde-led%20faction%2C%20while%20the%20one%20headed%20by%20Thackeray%20was%20called%20Shiv%20Sena%20(UBT)%20with%20a%20flaming%20torch%20as%20its%20symbol.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20July%20last%20year%2C%20the%20Ajit%20Pawar%20faction%20of%20the%20NCP%20also%20joined%20the%20Shinde-led%20government.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAssembly%20polls%20in%20Maharashtra%20are%20due%20in%20the%20second%20half%20of%202024.%20PTI%20PR%20CLS%20VT%20KRK%20GK%20NSK%20RSY%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Ci%3E(Except%20for%20the%20headline%2C%20this%20story%20has%20not%20been%20edited%20by%20NDTV%20staff%20and%20is%20published%20from%20a%20syndicated%20feed.)%3C%2Fi%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1704827220000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2023-11%2Fvsec1ssc_eknath-shinde-devendra-fadnavis-ani_625x300_01_November_23.jpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fmaharashtra-speaker-to-give-verdict-on-mlas-disqualification-requests-today-4830642%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22The%20political%20temperature%20rose%20in%20Maharashtra%20on%20Tuesday%20ahead%20of%20the%20crucial%20verdict%20by%20the%20assembly%20speaker%20on%20the%20cross-petitions%20by%20Shiv%20Sena%20factions%20seeking%20disqualification%20of%20each%20other's%20MLAs%20following%20a%20split%20in%20the%20party.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fmaharashtra-speaker-to-give-verdict-on-mlas-disqualification-requests-today-4830642%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww-ndtv-com.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fmaharashtra-speaker-to-give-verdict-on-mlas-disqualification-requests-today-4830642%2Famp%2F1%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fmaharashtra-speaker-to-give-verdict-on-mlas-disqualification-requests-today-4830642%2Famp%2F1%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22%E2%80%98In%20UK%2C%20Indians%20make%20up%20highest%20no.%20of%20int%E2%80%99l%20pupils%20plagiarising%20admission%20essays%E2%80%99%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1704827095000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.toiimg.com%2Fphoto%2Fmsid-106676943%2Cimgsize-979125.cms%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Findia%2Findians-make-up-highest-number-of-international-students-plagiarising-ucas-forms-in-uk%2Farticleshow%2F106676876.cms%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Number%20of%20students%20caught%20plagiarising%20personal%20statements%20on%20their%20undergraduate%20applications%20to%20British%20universities%20has%20doubled%20in%20the%20past%20two%20years%2C%20with%20highest%20number%20outside%20the%20UK%20coming%20from%20India.%20There%20were%207%2C300%20applications%20flagged%20for%20plagiarism%20in%202023%20and%203%2C559%20flagged%20in%202021%3B%20765%20of%20the%207%2C300%20in%202023%20were%20submitted%20by%20applicants%20from%20India%2C%20a%20spokesperson%20for%20Universities%20and%20Colleges%20Admissions%20Service%20(UCAS)%20said.%20The%20country%20of%20origin%20where%20plagiarism%20of%20personal%20statements%20is%20highest%2C%20outside%20the%20UK%2C%20is%20India%2C%20followed%20by%20Nigeria%2C%20Romania%20and%20China.%20according%20to%20UCAS.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22NAOMI%20CANTON%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonica