ll%20get%20everything%20investigated.%20If%20there%20has%20been%20any%20negligence%2C%20action%20will%20be%20taken%2C%26quot%3B%20Mr%20Vij%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20hospital%20authorities%20say%20they%20have%20formed%20a%20committee%20to%20investigate%20the%20issue.%20The%20report%20will%20be%20available%20in%20a%20couple%20of%20days%2C%20said%20Sangeeta%20Singla%2C%20the%20Principal%20Medical%20Officer%20of%20the%20city's%20Civil%20Hospital.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAsked%20what%20action%20will%20be%20taken%2C%20she%20said%2C%20%26quot%3BWe%20will%20give%20them%20a%20warning.%20Why%20the%20special%20case%20was%20not%20checked.%20If%20the%20patient%20was%20in%20such%20a%20state%20that%20she%20delivered%20on%20arrival%2C%20the%20staff%20on%20duty%20--%20doctors%2C%20nurses%20--%20should%20have%20been%20there%20to%20attend%20to%20her%2C%26quot%3B%20she%20told%20reporters.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1704826980000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-01%2F7cvs25oo_ambala-woman-gives-birth-_625x300_09_January_24.png%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Frefused-help-at-ambala-hospital-woman-gives-birth-outdoors-on-vegetable-cart-4832022%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22A%20woman%20gave%20birth%20to%20a%20baby%20on%20a%20vegetable%20cart%20on%20the%20premises%20of%20the%20government-run%20district%20hospital%20in%20Haryana's%20Ambala%20yesterday%20after%20the%20doctors%20allegedly%20refused%20to%20pay%20attention%20to%20her%20husband's%20repeated%20requests%20for%20help.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Frefused-help-at-ambala-hospital-woman-gives-birth-outdoors-on-vegetable-cart-4832022%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww-ndtv-com.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Frefused-help-at-ambala-hospital-woman-gives-birth-outdoors-on-vegetable-cart-4832022%2Famp%2F1%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Find