%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fentertainment%2Fhindi%2Fbollywood%2Fnews%2Fsamrat-prithviraj-director-reveals-akshay-kumar-had-tears-in-his-eyes-after-films-failure-had-creative-differences-with-aditya-chopra%2Farticleshow%2F106675669.cms%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Term%20Of%20Last%20Elected%20Body%20In%20J%26amp%3BK%20Ends%2C%20No%20Fresh%20Elections%20In%20Sight%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EThe%20curtain%20falls%20on%20the%20last%20vestige%20of%20elected%20representatives%20in%20Jammu%20and%20Kashmir%20as%20the%20term%20of%20over%2028%2C000%20panchayat%20members%20ended%20today%20with%20no%20fresh%20elections%20in%20sight.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20the%20absence%20of%20an%20elected%20government%20in%20the%20erstwhile%20state%20for%20more%20than%20five%20years%2C%20Panchayats-elected%20local%20bodies%20were%20the%20only%20democratic%20institutions%20functional%20in%20the%20region.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20administration%20of%20the%20Union%20Territory%20is%20likely%20to%20appoint%20administrators%20who%20will%20exercise%20the%20powers%20of%20grassroots%20elected%20bodies%20till%20the%20time%20fresh%20elections%20are%20held.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Jammu%20and%20Kashmir%20State%20Election%20Commission%20today%20announced%20a%20revision%20of%20electoral%20rolls%20which%20will%20be%20published%20by%20February%2026.%20It%20will%20be%20followed%20by%20a%20delimitation%20of%20Panchayats%20and%20reservation%20of%20seats%20for%20OBCs%2C%20sources%20told%20NDTV.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20State%20Election%20Commission%20will%20run%20a%20special%20campaign%20to%20undertake%20an%20annual%20summary%20revision%20of%20panchayat%20electoral%20rolls%2C%26quot%3B%20Jammu%20and%20Kashmir%20State%20Election%20Commissioner%2C%20BR%20Sharma%2C%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWhile%20the%20District%20Development%20Councils%20(%20DDC)%2C%20which%20is%20the%20third%20tier%20of%20the%20Panchayati%20Raj%20System%20will%20continue%20to%20function%2C%20they%20become%20meaningless%20in%20the%20absence%20of%20panchayats%20and%20block%20development%20councils.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EElections%20for%20the%20panchayats%20and%20Urban%20local%20bodies%20were%20last%20held%20in%20November%20and%20December%202018.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20the%20wake%20of%20an%20election%20boycott%20by%20the%20National%20Conference%20and%20the%20PDP%2C%20most%20of%20the%20panchayat%20members%20were%20elected%20unopposed.%20Around%2012%2C000%20seats%20remained%20vacant%20and%20were%20filled%20after%20the%20by-elections%20two%20years%20later%20in%202020.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAfter%20the%20completion%20of%20the%20five-year%20term%2C%20all%20the%20urban%20local%20bodies%20ceased%20to%20exist%20in%20December%20last%20month.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EJammu%20and%20Kashmir%20has%20been%20under%20direct%20Central%20rule%20since%20June%202018.%20Last%20month%2C%20the%20Supreme%20Court%20set%20the%20deadline%20for%20holding%20assembly%20elections%20before%20September%20this%20year.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1704820380000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2022-06%2F9k1e64a8_srinagar-generic-afp_625x300_02_June_22.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fterm-of-last-elected-body-in-jammu-and-kashmir-ends-no-fresh-elections-in-sight-4831676%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22The%20curtain%20falls%20on%20the%20last%20vestige%20of%20elected%20representatives%20in%20Jammu%20and%20Kashmir%20as%20the%20term%20of%20over%2028%2C000%20panchayat%20members%20ended%20today%20with%20no%20fresh%20elections%20in%20sight.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fterm-of-last-elected-body-in-jammu-and-kashmir-ends-no-fresh-elections-in-sight-4831676%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww-ndtv-com.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fterm-of-last-elected-body-in-jammu-and-kashmir-ends-no-fresh-elections-in-sight-4831676%2Famp%2F1%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fterm-of-last-elected-body-in-jammu-and-kashmir-ends-no-fresh-elections-in-sight-4831676%2Famp%2F1%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Start-Up%20CEO%20May%20Have%20Smothered%20Child%20With%20Pillow%3A%20Doctor%20After%20Autopsy%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EThe%20four-year-old%20son%20of%20the%20Bengaluru%20start-up%20founder%20Suchana%20Seth%20was%20smothered%20with%20a%20pillow%20and%20died%20of%20suffocation%2C%20doctors%20of%20Hiriyur%20Hospital%20said%20after%20preliminary%20examination%20of%20the%20body%20as%20it%20came%20for%20postmortem.%20The%20boy%2C%20who%20died%20in%20Goa%2C%20was%20taken%20to%20the%20Hiriyur%20Hospital%20mortuary%2C%20after%20his%20father%20returned%20from%20Indonesia.%20The%20child's%20mother%20has%20been%20arrested%20for%20the%20murder%20and%20is%20in%20police%20custody%20for%20questioning.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20child%20was%20smothered%2C%26quot%3B%20Dr%20Kumar%20Naik%2C%20who%20was%20in%20charge%20of%20the%20postmortem%20examination%2C%20told%20the%20media.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BHe%20could%20have%20probably%20died%20after%20being%20suffocated%20by%20a%20pillow%20or%20some%20other%20object.%20The%20child%20doesn't%20seem%20like%20he%20was%20killed%20by%20strangulation%20using%20hands.%20The%20killing%20took%20place%20over%2036%20hours%20ago.%20His%20face%20and%20chest%20are%20swollen%20due%20to%20suffocation.%20And%20the%20child's%20nose%20was%20bleeding%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%2039-year-old%20woman%20was%20caught%20from%20Karnataka's%20Chitradurga%20on%20Monday%20night%20while%20travelling%20with%20her%20son's%20body%20packed%20in%20a%20bag.%20%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20police%20said%20she%20is%20believed%20to%20have%20killed%20her%20son%20in%20a%20service%20apartment%20in%20Goa's%20Candolim%2C%20where%20they%20checked%20in%20on%20January%206.%20Then%20she%20tried%20suicide%20by%20slashing%20her%20wrist%2C%20the%20police%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBut%20her%20moves%20thereafter%20have%20raised%20a%20number%20of%20questions.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESuchana%20Seth%20said%20she%20wanted%20a%20taxi%20for%20a%20600-km%20journey%20to%20Bengaluru%2C%20brushing%20off%20the%20hotel%20authorities'%20suggestion%20that%20she%20take%20a%20flight.%20She%20told%20them%20her%20son%20was%20staying%20with%20a%20friend%20and%20gave%20an%20address%20that%20was%20later%20found%20to%20be%20fake.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20police%20are%20yet%20to%20zero-in%20on%20the%20motive%20for%20the%20murder.%20Suchana%20Seth%2C%20they%20said%2C%20is%20divorcing%20her%20husband%20and%20they%20had%20not%20parted%20on%20amicable%20terms.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20woman%20was%20arrested%20after%20the%20staff%20at%20the%20Sol%20Banyan%20Grande%20noticed%20bloodstains%20while%20cleaning%20the%20service%20apartment%20room%20and%20called%20in%20the%20police.%20The%20police%20contacted%20the%20driver%20of%20her%20cab%20and%20instructed%20him%20to%20head%20to%20the%20nearest%20police%20station.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1704820020000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-01%2Fkr8q1bso_suchana-seth_625x300_09_January_24.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fgoa-child-murder-bengaluru-ceo-start-up-ceo-suchana-seth-may-have-smothered-child-with-pillow-doctor-after-autopsy-4831595%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22The%20four-year-old%20son%20of%20the%20Bengaluru%20start-up%20founder%20Suchana%20Seth%20was%20smothered%20with%20a%20pillow%20and%20died%20of%20suffocation%2C%20doctors%20of%20Hiriyur%20Hospital%20said%20after%20preliminary%20examination%20of%20the%20body%20as%20it%20came%20for%20postmortem.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fgoa-child-murder-bengaluru-ceo-start-up-ceo-suchana-seth-may-have-smothered-child-with-pillow-doctor-after-autopsy-48