22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22This%20War%20Hero%20Fought%20Against%20Both%20China%20And%20Pak%2C%20Was%20Taken%20Prisoner%20In%20'62%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EBrigadier%20Amar%20Jit%20Singh%20Behl%2C%20a%20veteran%20of%20the%201962%20India-China%20war%2C%20died%20yesterday%20at%20the%20age%20of%2082%20at%20a%20military%20hospital%20in%20Haryana's%20Chandimandir.%20Brigadier%20AJS%20Behl%20(retired)%20was%20a%20decorated%20officer%20who%20fought%20gallantly%20against%20the%20Chinese%20during%20the%20Battle%20of%20Namka%20Chu%20in%20the%20northeast%20and%20witnessed%20action%20in%201965%20and%201971.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBrig%20Behl%20died%20due%20to%20age-related%20issues%20and%20the%20last%20rites%20will%20take%20place%20in%20Chandigarh.%20He%20was%20commissioned%20into%20the%20army%20in%201961%20as%20a%20second%20lieutenant%20and%20earned%20the%20prestigious%20maroon%20colours%20of%20the%20elite%20parachute%20regiment%20in%201962.%20In%20one%20of%20his%20interviews%20with%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.rediff.com%2Fnews%2Fslide-show%2Fslide-show-1-we-were-told-that-the-chinese-will-come-in-waves%2F20121017.htm%5C%22%3EClaude%20Arp%3C%2Fa%3Ei%2C%20a%20French%20historian%20and%20an%20expert%20on%20Tibet%20and%20China%2C%20Brig%20Behl%20talked%20about%20his%20journey%20from%20joining%20the%20Parachute%20Field%20Regiment%20to%20witnessing%20action%20in%20Arunachal%20Pradesh%2C%20erstwhile%20North%20East%20Frontier%20Agency%20(NEFA).%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHe%20joined%20the%2017%20Parachute%20Field%20Regiment%2C%20an%20artillery%20regiment%2C%20after%20completing%20an%20officer's%20course%20in%20July%201962%20in%20Agra.%20He%20underwent%20a%20gruelling%20test%20and%20training%20procedure.%20By%20September%201962%2C%20he%20was%20a%20%26quot%3Bfull-fledged%26quot%3B%20paratrooper%20with%20para%20wings.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%3E%3Cstrong%3EBattle%20Of%20Namka%20Chu%2C%201962%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBrig%20Behl%2C%20a%20young%20officer%20in%201962%2C%20was%20ordered%20to%20move%20forward%20in%20September%20and%20assist%20the%207%20Infantry%20Brigade%20under%20Brigadier%20John%20Dalvi%20deployed%20near%20Namka%20Chu%20River.%20He%20was%20a%20gun%20position%20officer%20(GPO)%20in%20the%20'E'%20troop%20and%20a%20battery%20of%20the%2036%20Mortar%20Regiment%20was%20already%20present%20with%207%20Infanry%20Bridage.%20The%20objective%20of%20the%20contentious%20'Forward%20Policy'%20was%20to%20evict%20the%20Chinese%20from%20the%20Thagla%20Ridge%20and%20establish%20forward%20posts%20close%20to%20the%20MacMohan%20line.%20The%20border%20demarcation%20was%20based%20on%20the%20watershed%20principle%20and%20contesting%20claims%20emerged%20on%20Thagla%20Ridge%2C%20a%20tri-junction%20between%20India%2C%20Bhutan%20and%20Tibet%2C%20which%20did%20not%20follow%20the%20principle.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EA%20troop%20with%20two%20officers%20-%20Captain%20HS%20Talwar%2C%202nd%20Lt%20Behl%2C%202%20Junior%20Commissioned%20Officers%20(JCOs)%20and%2045%20men%20were%20airlifted%20with%20four%2075mm%20howitzer%20guns.%20For%20three%20weeks%2C%20AJS%20Behl%20and%20his%20men%20were%20deployed%20on%20a%20plateau%20overlooking%20Namka%20Chu%2C%20which%20ended%20with%20the%20Chinese%20taking%20over%20the%20Indian%20posts%20and%20destroying%20the%207%20Infantry%20Brigade.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%3E%3Cstrong%3EOctober%2019%2C%201962%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Chinese%20lit%20a%20bonfire%20on%20October%2019%20to%20show%20their%20strength%20Brig.%20Behl%20told%20Claude%20Arpi%20in%20the%20interview%2C%20%26quot%3BWe%20could%20see%20them%20from%20naked%20eyes%2C%20they%20wanted%20us%20to%20see%20that%20they%20are%20there.%20On%20October%2019%2C%20the%20nursing%20assistant%20in%2017%20Para%20Field%20Regt.%20died%20due%20to%20pulmonary%20oedema%20and%20three%20more%20men%20died%20due%20to%20high%20altitude%20sickness%2C%20the%20communication%20lines%20were%20cut%20and%20the%20Chinese%20had%20cut%20us%20from%20the%20rear%20and%20I%20couldn't%20use%20the%20wireless%20due%20to%20the%20thick%20tress%20of%20Namka%20Chu.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20next%20morning%2C%20guns%20echoed%20in%20the%20mountain%20and%20the%20Chinese%20opened%20fire%20and%20heavy%20artillery%20shelling%20began%2C%20AJS%20Behl%20said%20in%20his%20account%20he%20wrote%20for%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.usiofindia.org%2Fpublication-journal%2F1962-war-battle-of-namka-chu-as-i-saw-it.html%5C%22%3EUnited%20Services%20Institute%20(USI)%3C%2Fa%3E.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThough%20we%20had%20no%20communication%20with%20anybody%2C%20I%20ordered%20my%20guns%20to%20start%20firing%20directly.%20There%20was%20a%20prominent%20area%2C%20the%20Black%20Rock%2C%20where%20we%20saw%20several%20Chinese%2C%20we%20kept%20firing%20there%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%20Brigadier%20John%20Dalvi%20in%20his%20book%2C%20The%20Himalayan%20Blunder%2C%20described%20the%20valour%20displayed%20by%20the%2017%20Para%20Field%20Regiment.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAJS%20Behl%20and%20his%20men%20were%20taken%20as%20prisoners%20of%20war%20(POW)%20by%20the%20Chinese.%20%26quot%3BFrom%20proud%20paratroopers%2C%20we%20were%20now%20POWs%20of%20the%20Chinese%26quot%3B%20at%20Tsangdhar%2C%20he%20said%2C%20adding%20that%20it%20was%20a%20%26quot%3Bbig%20shock%26quot%3B%20to%20him.%20On%20October%2022%2C%20AJS%20Behl%20said%20he%20buried%20the%20bodies%20of%20his%20men.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHe%20was%20repatriated%20after%20seven%20months%20and%20handed%20over%20to%20the%20Indian%20Red%20Cross%20in%20Bumla.%20He%20was%20later%20posted%20back%20to%20the%2017%20Parachute%20Field%20Regiment.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAJS%20Behl%20saw%20action%20three%20years%20later%20in%20the%20Rann%20of%20Kutch%20in%20Gujarat.%20Pakistan%20launched%20Operation%20Desert%20Hawk%20in%20April%20and%20infiltrated%20around%2010%20km%20inside%20Indian%20territory.%20A%20UK-brokered%20ceasefire%20diffused%20tensions%20only%20to%20get%20reignited%20four%20months%20la