0be%20firm%20and%20take%20it%20forward%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EFor%20the%20Congress%2C%20seat%20sharing%20discussions%20are%20not%20likely%20to%20be%20a%20cakewalk%2C%20given%20its%20troubled%20relationship%20with%20a%20string%20of%20Opposition%20parties%20including%20the%20Samajwadi%20Party%2C%20Arvind%20Kejriwal's%20Aam%20Aadmi%20Party%20and%20the%20Trinamool%20Congress.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAll%20three%20parties%20have%20indicated%20that%20they%20are%20not%20open%20to%20sharing%2C%20especially%20the%20Samajwadi%20Party%20after%20being%20rebuffed%20in%20Madhya%20Pradesh.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20SP%2C%20which%20had%20asked%20for%20six%20seats%20in%20the%20assembly%20elections%20as%20a%20pilot%20run%20for%20seat%20sharing%2C%20was%20turned%20down%20by%20then%20state%20party%20chief%20Kamal%20Nath%2C%20who%20later%20was%20sacked%20over%20the%20party's%20rout.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20Bengal%20too%2C%20Trinamool%20Congress%20chief%20and%20Chief%20Minister%20Mamata%20Banerjee%20had%20claimed%20that%20it%20was%20her%20party%20that%20stands%20the%20best%20chance%20against%20the%20BJP%20in%20the%20state.%20Mr%20Khurshid%20today%20said%20they%20had%20got%20in%20touch%20with%20Derek%20O'Brien%2C%20%26quot%3Bwho%20was%20very%20gracious%26quot%3B%2C%20and%20expressed%20hope%20that%20something%20might%20still%20be%20worked%20out.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20Bengal%2C%20Congress%20would%20like%20to%20have%20five%20seats.%20But%20Trinamool%20Congress%20chief%20and%20Chief%20Minister%20Mamata%20Banerjee%20has%20made%20it%20clear%20that%20she%20is%20not%20ready%20to%20offer%20any.%20The%20matter%20has%20not%20been%20officially%20discussed%20yet.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ECongress's%20discussion%20with%20AAP%20is%20also%20proving%20contentious.%20While%20the%20party%20wants%20four%20seats%20in%20Delhi%20and%20seven%20seats%20in%20Punjab%2C%20AAP%20is%20not%20ready%20to%20comply.%20In%20both%20Delhi%20and%20Punjab%2C%20the%20ruling%20party%20wants%20the%20bigger%20share%20of%20seats.%20AAP%20also%20wants%20to%20contest%20in%20Goa%2C%20Haryana%20and%20Gujarat%2C%20sources%20said.%20%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20Bihar%2C%20the%20Congress%20and%20the%20Rashtriya%20Janata%20Dal%20have%20conducted%20the%20preliminary%20talks.%20Nitish%20Kumar's%20Janata%20Dal%20United%20will%20not%20settle%20for%20less%20than%2017%20of%20the%20state's%2040%20seats.%20It%20is%20likely%20that%20the%20RJD%20would%20also%20contest%2017%20seats%20in%20line%20with%20the%202015%20assembly%20polls%20formula.%20Five%20seats%20can%20go%20to%20the%20Congress%20and%20one%20to%20the%20CPI-ML.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1704811560000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2023-05%2Fk8oc986k_maha-vikas-aghadi-meeting-pti_625x300_14_May_23.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Findia-bloc-seat-sharing-settled-in-maharashtra-on-track-in-up-congress-4830834%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Maharashtra's%20Maha%20Vikas%20Aghadi%20--%20an%20alliance%20of%20Shiv%20Sena%20UBT%2C%20Sharad%20Pawar's%20Nationalist%20Congress%20Party%20and%20the%20Congress%20--%20have%20come%20to%20an%20understanding%20on%20the%20division%20of%20the%20state's%2048%20seats.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Findia-bloc-seat-sharing-settled-in-maharashtra-on-track-in-up-congress-4830834%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww-ndtv-com.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Findia-bloc-seat-sharing-settled-in-maharashtra-on-track-in-up-congress-4830834%2Famp%2F1%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Findia-bloc-seat-sharing-settled-in-maharashtra-on-track-in-up-congress-4830834%2Famp%2F1%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Katrina%20shares%20quirky%20wish%20for%20Farah%20on%20her%20b'day%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1704811187000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.toiimg.com%2Fphoto%2Fmsid