nment%20192%20companies%20of%20the%20central%20forces%2C%20paramilitary%20forces%2C%20which%20amount%20to%20about%2011%20to%2012%2C000%20armed%20people%2C%20asking%20them%20to%20make%20use%20of%20them%2C%20because%20the%20Constitution%20doesn%E2%80%99t%20allow%20the%20forces%20to%20act%20on%20their%20own.%20Asking%20them%20to%20make%20use%20of%20them%2C%20they%20are%20near%20at%20hand.%20In%20fact%2C%20it%20could%20have%20been%20done%20very%20easily%2C%20if%20there%20had%20been%20any%20will%20on%20the%20part%20of%20the%20state%20government.%20They%20were%20in%20Faizabad.%20This%20was%20happening%20in%20Ayodhya.%20I%20mean%2C%20just%20within%205%20minutes%2C%2010%20minutes%2C%20everything%20could%20have%20been%20controlled%20so%20that%20was%20the%20situation.%20Not%20only%20not%20making%20use%20of%20them%20but%20going%20to%20the%20Supreme%20Court%20and%20asking%20that%20the%20central%20forces%20be%20withdrawn%2C%20making%20protests%20going%20from%20place%20to%20place%2C%20asking%20the%20central%20forces%20to%20vacate%20the%20premises%20they%20were%20occupying%20within%202%20hours%2C%20giving%20them%20notices.%20Now%20this%20is%20the%20kind%20of%20thing%20that%20has%20happened%20and%20as%20a%20result%20of%20this%2C%20the%20situation%20went%20out%20of%20control.%20In%20fact%2C%20they%20didn%E2%80%99t%20want%20to%20control%20it%20in%20any%20case.%20There%20were%20orders%20from%20the%20chief%20minister%20that%20no%20force%20should%20be%20used.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cb%3EBut%20if%2C%20as%20you%20say%2C%20they%20did%20not%20want%20to%20control%20it%20in%20any%20case%2C%20they%20were%20not%20cooperating%2C%20why%20did%20you%20not%20dismiss%20them%20%5Bthe%20BJP%20state%20government%20in%20UP%5D%20before%20December%20the%206th%3F%3C%2Fb%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3ENo%20it%20is%20not%20possible%2C%20because%20they%20have%20been%20telling%20the%20courts%2C%20telling%20the%20National%20Integration%20Council%2C%20telling%20the%20whole%20world%2C%20as%20a%20government%2C%20they%20would%20do%20it%20under%20any%20circumstances.%20This%20was%20the%20commitment%20they%20were%20giving%20to%20the%20whole%20world.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cb%3EAnd%20you%20trusted%20them.%3C%2Fb%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EWell%2C%20the%20state%20government%20has%20to%20be%20trusted%20by%20the%20central%20government.%20If%20anyone%20can%20tell%20me%20about%20any%20other%20kind%20of%20relationship%20or%20particularly%20a%20relationship%20of%20total%20mistrust%20between%20the%20state%20government%20and%20the%20central%20government%2C%20I%20would%20very%20respectfully%20disagree%20that%20it%20is%20not%20possible%20under%20a%20Federal%20Constitution%20like%20India.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cb%3EI%20accept%20the%20point%20of%20making%20prime%20minister%2C%20but%20there%20is%20the%20opposite%20that%20can%20be%20said%20also.%20This%20is%20a%20party%2C%20the%20BJP%20that%20has%20whipped%20up%20emotions%2C%20as%20you%20have%20often%20argued%20on%20the%20basis%20of%20religion%20before.%20The%20state%20government%20was%20refusing%20to%20cooperate%20with%20you%20this%20time%20around%20and%20they%20are%20the%20opposition%2C%20so%20why%20trust%20them%3F%C2%A0%3C%2Fb%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3ENo%2C%20the%20question%20is%20what%20do%20you%20do%20if%20you%20don%E2%80%99t%20trust%20them.%20You%20cannot%20dismiss%20that%20government%20while%20the%20government%20is%20shouting%20from%20the%20house%20tops%20that%20it%20is%20prepared%20to%20discharge%20its%20constitutional%20responsibility%2C%20never%20mind%20which%20party.%20The%20point%20is%20whether%20the%20state%20government%20as%20such%20is%20doing%20its%20duty%20or%20not%2C%20promising%20to%20do%20its%20duty%20or%20not%2C%20making%20preparations%20for%20it%20or%20not.%20I%20have%20done%20the%20utmost%20I%20could%20do%20by%20making%20available%20a%20very%20large%20force%20which%20could%20have%20been%20made%20use%20of%2C%20at%20a%20moment%E2%80%99s%20notice.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3