3ENo%2C%20I%20don%E2%80%99t%20think%20we%20could%20have%20used%20356%20earlier.%20I%E2%80%99m%20quite%20sure%20about%20that.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cb%3EIn%20hindsight%20though%2C%20would%20you%20have%20preferred%20now%20to%20have%20used%20355%20then%3F%C2%A0%3C%2Fb%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EI%20don%E2%80%99t%20want%20to%20go%20by%20hindsight%20at%20all.%20I%20would%20like%20to%20do%20what%20is%20possible%2C%20what%20is%20necessary%20at%20the%20moment.%20That%20is%20how%20a%20government%20works.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cb%3EDo%20you%20feel%2C%20prime%20minister%2C%20that%20the%20attitude%20of%20accommodation%2C%20that%20the%20attitude%20of%20understanding%20that%20you%20had%20shown%20the%20BJP%2C%20now%20was%20mistaken%20or%20that%20they%20misled%20you%3F%C2%A0%3C%2Fb%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EI%20don%E2%80%99t%20think%20it%20was%20mistaken.%20You%20see%20democracy%20can%20never%20run%20on%20the%20basis%20of%20total%20mistrust%20of%20parties%20or%20governments.%20The%20point%20is%2C%20you%20do%20get%20into%20difficulties%2C%20you%20have%20to%20get%20over%20the%20difficulties%2C%20learn%20a%20few%20things%20about%20other%20parties%20but%20even%20then%2C%20you%20see%2C%20the%20Constitution%20of%20India%20has%20a%20certain%20unity%20of%20its%20own%20and%20you%20cannot%20act%20in%20a%20manner%20which%20disrupts%20the%20acting%2C%20the%20functioning%20of%20the%20Constitution.%20I%20think%20that%20is%20a%20lesson%20which%20everyone%20has%20to%20bear%20in%20mind.%20That%20is%20a%20principle%20which%20everyone%20has%20to%20bear%20in%20mind.%20I%20cannot%20become%20unprincipled%20and%20violate%20the%20constitution%20because%20somebody%20else%20has%20done%20it.%20I%20mean%2C%20I%20don%E2%80%99t%20think%20anyone%20can%20recommend%20that%20or%20commend%20that.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cb%3EYour%20home%20minister%20has%20at%20least%20twice%20spoken%20of%20a%20contingency%20plan%20which%20he%20said%20he%20had.%C2%A0%3C%2Fb%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThis%20was%20a%20contingency%20plan.%20Giving%20them%20the%20force%20that%20they%20need%2C%20in%20case%20of%20need%2C%20they%20have%20to%20use%20it%2C%20asking%20them%20to%20use%20it%2C%20and%20telling%20them%2C%20time%20and%20again%2C%20every%20hour%2C%20to%20use%20it.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cb%3EBut%20when%20they%2C%20but%20was%20there%20a%20plan%20which%20could%20have%20been%20activated%20when%20you%20realised%20that%20they%20were%20not%20using%20the%20force%20you%20had%20made%20available%20and%20that%20things%20were%20going%20out%20of%20control%3F%3C%2Fb%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EWell%2C%20this%20is%20what%20I%E2%80%99m%20saying.%20You%20see%2C%20you%20have%20to%20go%20up%20to%20a%20point%20in%20trusting%20the%20state%20government.%20There%20is%20no%20way%20you%20can%20say%20that%20you%20are%20not%20going%20to%20do%20it.%20Therefore%2C%20for%20every%20step%2C%20I%20have%20a%20counter%20step%20%E2%80%93%20this%20kind%20of%20thing%20will%20not%20do.%20The%20moment%20our%20forces%20were%20sent%20there%2C%20the%20protest%20that%20came%20from%20the%20government%20of%20Uttar%20Pradesh%20and%20the%20BJP%20everywhere%2C%20including%20the%20Supreme%20Court%2C%20they%20have%20to%20be%20seen%20to%20understand%20what%20it%20was%20even%20to%20send%20forces%20there.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cb%3ELet%E2%80%99s%20just%20talk%20a%20little%20about%20the%20forces%2C%20prime%20minister.%20By%20all%20newspaper%20accounts%2C%20the%20demolition%20began%20just%20before%20midday%20and%20it%20lasted%20for%20some%20five%20hours.%20Why%20was%20it%20not%20possible%20for%20your%20government%20to%20act%20during%20that%20time%3F%C2%A0%3C%2Fb%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EYes%2C%20these%20hours%20have%20been%20noted.%20What%20happened%20at%20what%20time%20has%20been%20noted.%20We%20are%20coming%20out%20with%20a%20white%20paper%20on%20that.%20I%20will%20give%20you%20that%2C%20that%20gives%20you%20all%20the%20details%2C%20but%20in%20short%2C%20I%20could%20tell%20you%20that%20it%20was%20known%20to%20us%20only%20after%201%3A00.%20We%20have%2C%20we%20asked%20them%2C%20they%20said%20we%20want%2025%20companies.%2025%20companies%20were%20immediately%20made%20available.%20Then%20again%2C%20they%20said%20we%20want%2050%20companies.%20They%20were%20also%20made%20available.%20In%20short%2C%20when%20they%20were%20on%20their%20way%20to%20Ayodhya%2C%20they%20were%20stopped%20in%20the%20middle.%20There%20were%20200%2C000%20people%20milling%20around.%20The%20magistrate%20said%2C%20%E2%80%9CI%20am%20under%20strict%20orders%20of%20the%20chief%20minister%20that%20force%20should%20not%20be%20used.%20Now%20you%20cannot%20proceed%20without%20using%20force.%20Therefore%2C%20I%20will%20not%20allow%20you%20to%20use%20force.%20You%20please%20go%20back%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cb%3ESo%2C%20do%20you%20have%20the%20impression%20that%20the%20chief%20minister%20was%20saying%20different%20things%20to%20you%20and%20different%20things%20to%20the%20magistrate%3F%C2%A0%3C%2Fb%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EAbsolutely.%20Absolutely.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cb%3EHe%20was%20actually%20playing%20tricks%2C%20to%20coin%20a%20phrase.%3C%2Fb%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EWell%2C%20phraseology%20is%20yours%2C%20but%20I%20am%20telling%20you%20what%20happened.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cb%3EAnd%20you%E2%80%99re%20not%20disagreeing%20with%20the%20phraseology.%C2%A0%3C%2Fb%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EWell%2C%20why%20should%20I%3F%20It%20is%20your%20phraseology%2C%20but%20so%20long%20as%20the%20substance%20is%20the%20same.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cb%3EOne%20other%20thing%2C%20prime%20minister.%20The%20actual%20assault%20on%20the%20Masjid%20proper%20began%20around%20midday%2C%20but%20your%20forces%20didn%E2%80%99t%20clear%20it%20till%20some%2016%20hours%20later.%20Although%20when%20they%20did%2C%20they%20did%20so%20without%20loss%20of%20life.%20Why%20was%20that%20clearance%20direct%20action%20not%20possible%3F%3C%2Fb%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20man%20on%20the%20spot%20who%20was%20in%20charge%20of%20the%20operations%20said%20that%20they%20could%20do%20it%20in%20the%20night%2C%20not%20during%20the%20day%2C%20when%20still%20150%2C000%20people%20were%20milling%20around.%20He%20waited%20for%20the%20night%20and%20then%20made%20the%20assault.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cins%3EAlso%20read%3A%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fpolitics%2Fayodhyas-class-of-1992-the-key-conspirators%5C%22%3EAyodhya%E2%80%99s%20Class%20of%201992%3A%20The%20Key%20Conspirators%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fins%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cb%3ESo%2C%20the%20timing%20of%20the%20assault%20was%20decided%20by%20the%20man%20on%20the%20spot.%C2%A0%3C%2Fb%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EFor%20strategic%20reasons%2C%20yes.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cb%3EThere%E2%80%99s%20no%20political%20connection%2C%20not%20at%20all%2C%20whatsoever%3F%3C%2Fb%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3ENot%20at%20all.%20In%20fact%20we%20were%20asking%20him%20to%20do%20it%20all%20the%20time%2C%20but%20he%20said%20no%2C%20I%20will%20have%20to%20do%20it%20only%20in%20the%20night%2C%20after%20nightfall.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cb%3EWhy%20did%20your%20government%20not%20stop%20the%20yatras%20that%20went%20on%20for%20a%20week%20prior%2C%20led%20by%20Mr%20Advani%20and%20Dr%20Joshi%2C%20when%20it%20was%20quite%20clear%20that%20they%20were%20whipping%20up%20emotions%20and%20creating%20tension%3F%C2%A0%3C%2Fb%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EIn%20this%20country%2C%20we%20don%E2%80%99t%20stop%20yatras%20just%20for%20stopping%20them.%20Mr%20Murali%20Manohar%20Joshi%20also%20went%20on%20a%20yatra%2C%20all%20India%20yatra%2C%20we%20did%20not%20stop.%20Everyone%20can%20go%20everywhere.%20I%20mean%20there%20is%20no%20stopping%20this%20and%20in%20fact%2C%20if%20we%20had%20stopped%20the%20yatras%2C%20we%20were%20not%20quite%20sure%20that%20things%20would%20not%20have%20worsened.%20I%20mean%2C%20he%E2%80%99s%20a%20leader%20of%20stature.%20He%20is%20going%2C%20we%20think%20that%20he%20is%20going%2C%20I%20mean%20he%20says%20he%20is%20going%20to%20control%2C%20he%20is%20also%20making%20fairy%20speeches.%20We%20know%20what%20is%20happening%20at%20the%20moment%2C%20at%20that%20moment.%20We%20are%20watching%20but%20we%20cannot%20really%20stop%20the%20yatra.%20Have%20you%20ever%20seen%20a%20yatra%20where%20thousands%20and%20thousands%20of%20people%20are%20participating%20being%20stopped%3F%20You%20mean%20a%20blood%20bath%20there%20on%20that%20same%20spot!%20And%20how%20do%20we%20enter%20Uttar%20Pradesh%3F%20Who%20is%20in%20charge%20of%20law%20and%20order%20in%20Uttar%20Pradesh%3F%20Who%20is%20in%20charge%20of%20stopping%20the%20yatra%3F%20Am%20I%20in%20charge%3F%20Is%20the%20home%20minister%20of%20India%20in%20charge%3F%20Why%20don%E2%80%99t%20you%20ask%20yourself%20that%20question%3F%20The%20yatra%20starts%20from%20Mathura.%20Mathura%20is%20in%20Uttar%20Pradesh.%20Law%20and%20order%20is%20Uttar%20Pradesh%20government%E2%80%99s%20job%2C%20not%20mine.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cb%3EWhy%20did%20your%20government%20not%20try%20and%20limit%20the%20congregation%20that%20assembled%3F%20There%20were%20some%203%20lakh%20Kar%20Sevaks%20by%20some%20account%20who%20were%20there.%20Could%20you%20not%20have%20limited%20that%20number%3F%C2%A0%3C%2Fb%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EIt%20did%20not%20work%20in%201990.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cb%3EBut%20it%20could%20have%20been%20tried%20in%201992.%C2%A0%3C%2Fb%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3ENo%2C%20it%20could%20not%20have%20been%20tried%20because%20you%20cannot%20stop%20people%20from%20going%20anywhere.%20You%20see%2C%20you%20do%20not%20know%20what%20they%20are%20going%20to%20do.%20The%20point%20is%20that%20if%20there%20is%20a%20yatra%2C%20if%20there%20is%20a%20religious%20fervour%2C%20somebody%20wants%20to%20go%20and%20do%20kar%20seva.%20According%20to%20the%20definition%20given%20by%20the%20Supreme%20Court%2C%20it%E2%80%99s%20not%20as%20if%20all%20kar%20seva%20was%20banned.%20The%20Supreme%20Court%20gave%20the%20parameters%20of%20this%20Kar%20Seva%20and%20they%20were%20going%20to%20do%20just%20that.%20That%20is%20what%20everybody%20knew%20about%20the%20kar%20seva.%20How%20do%20you%20think%20anybody%20will%20stop%20or%20can%20stop%20any%20kar%20seva%3F%20Kar%20seva%20was%20very%20clearly%20delimited%20by%20the%20Supreme%20Court.%20What%20all%20you%20want%20to%20say%20is%20I%20should%20have%20done%20it%20in%20spite%20of%20it.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cb%3EBut%20what%20do%20you%20say%20to%20someone%20who%20hears%20you%20and%20says%20he%E2%80%99s%20given%20lots%20of%20reasons%20why%20he%20couldn%E2%80%99t%20stop%20the%20yatras%2C%20he%E2%80%99s%20given%20lots%20of%20reasons%20why%20he%20couldn%E2%80%99t%20stop%20the%20congregation%20in%20Ayodhya%20growing%20to%20five%20lakhs%2C%20but%20in%20every%20case%20he%20seems%20to%20be%20pleading%20helplessness.%3C%2Fb%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EI%E2%80%99m%20not%20pleading%20helplessness%20at%20all.%20I%20am%20only%20saying%20that%20I%20am%20under%20the%20Constitution%2C%20acting%20under%20the%20Constitution.%20The%20moment%20I%20was%20able%20to%20act%20under%20the%20Constitution%2C%20I%20acted.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-caption%5C%22%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%20709px)%2085vw%2C%20(max-width%3A%20909px)%2067vw%2C%20(max-width%3A%201362px)%2062vw%2C%20840px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2019%2F11%2F10102847%2Fclass-of-92.jpg%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2019%2F11%2F10102847%2Fclass-of-92.jpg%201200w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2019%2F11%2F10102847%2Fclass-of-92-300x150.jpg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2019%2F