3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EI%20too%20feel%20the%20same%20kind%20of%20betrayal%20has%20happened%2C%20not%20only%20to%20them%2C%20not%20only%20to%20me%2C%20to%20the%20whole%20nation.%20I%20have%20all%20sympathy%20and%20love%20for%20them.%20I%20feel%20exactly%20as%20they%20feel%2C%20the%20same%20distress%20and%20the%20same%20anguish%2C%20but%20I%20would%20like%20to%20embrace%20them%20and%20tell%20them%20that%20we%20will%20face%20this%20danger%20together.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cb%3EHow%20do%20you%2C%20as%20prime%20minister%20of%20India%2C%20react%20to%20the%20demolition%20and%20destruction%20of%20Hindu%20temples%20in%20Pakistan%20and%20Bangladesh%20and%20the%20attack%20on%20Indian%20diplomatic%20property%3F%C2%A0%3C%2Fb%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EMy%20reaction%20is%20the%20same%20whether%20it%20is%20a%20Hindu%20temple%20or%20a%20Muslim%20Mosque%20or%20any%20other%20denomination.%20The%20desecration%20or%20destruction%20of%20places%20of%20worship%20is%20a%20heinous%20crime.%20It%20should%20not%20be%20done%20anywhere%20and%20whoever%20does%20it%20is%20really%20doing%20a%20great%20disservice%20to%20not%20only%20all%20religions%20but%20to%20mankind%20itself.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cb%3EWhat%20about%20the%20fact%20that%20the%20Pakistan%20High%20Commission%20in%20Delhi%20has%20been%20flying%20its%20flag%20at%20half%20mast%3F%20What%20do%20you%20say%20about%20that%3F%C2%A0%3C%2Fb%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EAbout%20what%3F%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cb%3EThey%20have%20flown%2C%20in%20the%20capital%20of%20India%2C%20their%20flag%20at%20their%20High%20Commission%20in%20Shantipath%20at%20half%20mast.%3C%2Fb%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EI%20must%20check%20on%20that.%20I%20must%20check%20on%20that.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cb%3EIt%20was%20done%20as%20a%20deliberate%20attempt%20to%20show%20sympathy%20with%20the%20Muslim%20community%20in%20India%20for%20what%20happened.%3C%2Fb%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EIt%20doesn%E2%80%99t%20have%20to%20be.%20I%20mean%2C%20it%20is%20being%20done%20everywhere%20by%20Pakistan.%20Pakistan%20is%20heading%20this%20campaign.Everyone%20knows%20that.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cb%3EDo%20you%2C%20as%20prime%20minister%20of%20India%2C%20resent%20the%20fact%20that%20they%20are%20using%20this%20politically%3F%3C%2Fb%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EOf%20course%2C%20I%20resent%20it.%20I%20have%20expressed%20it%20several%20times.%20I%20have%20made%20it%20absolutely%20clear%20that%20this%20is%20not%20on%20but%20this%20is%20going%20on.%20This%20is%20what%20the%20unfortunate%20part%20is.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cb%3EOne%20last%20question%2C%20prime%20minister.%20You%20spoke%20about%20duty%20but%20when%20you%20first%20came%20to%20office%20as%20prime%20minister%2C%20you%20defined%20your%20duty%20as%20putting%20India%E2%80%99s%20economy%20back%20on%20the%20rails.%C2%A0%3C%2Fb%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EYes.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cb%3EAnd%20you%20did%20so%20by%20launching%20some%20of%20the%20most%20far-reaching%20economic%20reforms.%20Now%20it%E2%80%99s%20widely%20believed%2C%20in%20the%20light%20of%20what%E2%80%99s%20happened%2C%20they%E2%80%99ve%20either%20been%20shelved%20or%20they%E2%80%99ve%20been%20forgotten%20about%20or%20derailed.%20Is%20that%20so%3F%C2%A0%3C%2Fb%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EWell%2C%20I%20think%20none%20of%20these%20is%20true.%20Neither%20derailed%20nor%20shelved%20nor%20forgotten.%20The%20only%20thing%20is%20you%20have%20only%20one%20event%20that%20hits%20the%20headlines.%20No%20event%20hits%20the%20headlines%20always.%20I%20mean%2C%20today%20Ayodhya%20has%20hit%20the%20headlines.%20After%20a%20few%20days%2C%20it%20will%20no%20longer%20hit%20the%20headlines.%20We%20will%20go%20back%20to%20our%20economic%20program.%20In%20fact%2C%20the%20economic%20program%20is%20on.%20There%20has%20been%20no%20Interruption%20whatsoever.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cins%3EAlso%20read%3A%C2%A0%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fpolitics%2Fthe-provocateur-in-chief-l-k-advani%5C%22%3EThe%20Provocateur%20in%20Chief%20%E2%80%93%20L.K.%20Advani%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fins%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cb%3ESo%20all%20the%20speculation%20is%20unfounded.%3C%2Fb%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EAbsolutely%20unfounded.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cb%3EYou%20say%20after%20a%20few%20days.%20So%2C%20can%20you%20give%20me%20an%20indication%2C%20will%20we%20see%20economic%20reforms%20before%20the%20year%20is%20up%2C%20more%20economic%20reforms%3F%C2%A0%3C%2Fb%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EWell%2C%20what%20I%E2%80%99m%20saying%20is%20the%20process%20of%20economic%20reforms%20has%20not%20stopped.%20It%20will%20not%20stop%20because%20once%20you%20do%20the%20essentials%2C%20there%20is%20not%20very%20much%20more%20to%20do.%20You%20have%20to%20do%20a%20few%20things%20here%20and%20there%20by%20way%20of%20maintaining%20the%20pace%20etc.%2C%20which%20is%20being%20done%2C%20but%20that%20is%20not%20noticed%20because%20that%20becomes%20routinised.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cb%3EBut%20just%20as%20committed%20to%20things%20like%20an%20exit%20policy%20to%20freeing%20the%20exchange%20rate%20to%20financial%20reforms%20of%20banks%3F%3C%2Fb%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EAll%20those%20matters%20are%20being%20examined.%20You%20see%20there%20is%20no%20such%20thing%20as%20an%20exit%20policy%20properly%20so%20called.%20What%20we%20are%20doing%20here%20through%20the%20national%20renewal%20fund%20is%20to%20see%20that%20wherever%20it%20is%20necessary%20to%20bring%20a%20a%20particular%20industry%20back%20to%20health.%20We%20take%20several%20measures.%20Out%20of%20those%20measures%2C%20reduction%20of%20the%20workforce%20is%20one%20and%20when%20that%20happens%2C%20we%20will%20have%20to%20see%20that%20it%20is%20is%20done%20with%20a%20human%20face.%20We%20will%20have%20to%20see%20that%20no%20one%20is%20thrown%20on%20the%20street%20without%20a%20job.%20In%20this%20country%20that%20should%20not%20happen%20and%20that%20aspect%20is%20being%20taken%20care%20of.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cb%3EMy%20last%20question%2C%20prime%20minister%2C%20addressed%20particularly%20to%20those%20who%20are%20supporters%20of%20yours.%20They%20look%20at%20you%20and%20they%20say%20the%20prime%20minister%E2%80%99s%20in%20a%20no-win%20situation.%20If%20he%20is%20strong%20and%20tough%20with%20the%20BJP%2C%20he%20could%20polarise%20the%20situation%20and%20make%20matters%20worse.%20If%20he%20doesn%E2%80%99t%20take%20strong%20action%2C%20he%E2%80%99ll%20lose%20the%20Muslim%20community.%3C%2Fb%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EI%20am%20not%20in%20a%20no-win%20situation.%20I%20am%20not%20really%20out%20to%20win%20communities.%20I%20am%20out%20to%20do%20my%20duty%20and%20that%20is%20the%20duty%20of%20secularism.%20I%20have%20to%20see%20that%20this%20country%20is%20held%20together.%20I%20do%20not%20really%20calculate%20what%20is%20going%20to%20happen%20tomorrow.%20I%20am%20calculating%20what%20is%20to%20happen%20in%20the%20long%20run%20and%20that%20is%20my%20real%20concern.%20This%20India%20should%20remain%20should%20live%20forever%20for%20the%20coming%20generations.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cb%3EAnd%20the%20Congress%20party%20and%20%E2%80%A6%3C%2Fb%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20Congress%20party%20is%20solidly%20behind%20this.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cb%3EThe%20cabinet%20as%20well%3F%C2%A0%3C%2Fb%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20cabinet%2C%20the%20Congress%20party%2C%20every%20Congressman%20in%20this%20country%20is%20behind%20this.%20No%20one%20wants%20anything%20else%20done%20or%20anything%20different%20done.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cb%3EIn%20which%20case%20there%20is%20no%20question%20of%20Mr%20Narasimha%20Rao%20resigning%20as%20prime%20minister%20of%20India%E2%80%A6%3C%2Fb%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EWhy%20should%20I%3F%20There%E2%80%99s%20no%20question.%20No