20allowed%20to%20be%20there%20with%20100%20people%2C%20I%20wouldn%E2%80%99t%20have%20gone%20there%20that%20day.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWhile%20the%20Shankaracharya%20praised%20Prime%20Minister%20Modi%20for%20his%20commitment%20towards%20Hindutva%2C%20he%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.newindianexpress.com%2Fnation%2F2024%2Fjan%2F05%2Fpuri-seer-says-wont-visit-ayodhya-says-rituals-must-conform-to-shastras-2648076.html%5C%22%3Etold%3C%2Fa%3E%20the%20%3Cem%3ENew%20Indian%20Express%3C%2Fem%3E%2C%20%E2%80%9CThe%20pilgrimages%20are%20now%20being%20turned%20into%20centres%20of%20tourism%20in%20the%20name%20of%20development%2C%20which%20means%20that%20Teerth%20Sthals%20are%20being%20turned%20into%20Bhog%20Sthals%2C%20perhaps%20this%20what%20is%20being%20lapped%20up%20by%20the%20people%20also%20in%20the%20name%20of%20development.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EFour%20Shankaracharyas%20have%20refused%20to%20participate%20in%20the%20organisation%20of%20Ram%20temple%2C%20%3Cem%3EThe%20Wire%3C%2Fem%3E%20reported.%20Academic%2C%20author%2C%20and%20commentator%20Apoorvanand%20pointed%20out%20that%20although%20it%E2%80%99s%20said%20to%20be%20a%20non-religious%20event%2C%20it%20is%20perceived%20as%20a%20political%20event%20for%20the%20BJP.%20He%20questioned%20why%20the%20Congress%20or%20other%20parties%20cannot%20articulate%20this%20straightforward%20observation.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3E%E2%80%9CHum%20anti-Modi%20nahi%20hain%2C%20lekin%20hum%20anti-dharamashashtra%20bhi%20nahi%20hona%20chahte%3C%2Fem%3E%20(We%20are%20not%20anti-Modi%2C%20but%20we%20do%20not%20want%20to%20be%20anti-%3Cem%3Edharamashashtra%3C%2Fem%3E%20either)%2C%E2%80%9D%20one%20of%20the%20Shankaracharyas%2C%20Jyotishpeeth%E2%80%99s%20Shankaracharya%20Swami%20Avimukteshwaranand%2C%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3E%E2%80%9CShankaracharyo%20ka%20daitwa%20hain%20ki%20wo%20shashtra%20vidhi%20ka%20palan%20karein%20aur%20karwayein.%20Ab%20wahan%20par%20shashtra%20vidhi%20ki%20upeksha%20ho%20rahi%20hain.%20Sabse%20pehli%20upeksha%20hain%20ki%20mandir%20abhi%20pura%20bana%20nahi%20hain%2C%20aur%20pratishtha%20ki%20ja%20rahi%20hain.%20Koi%20aisi%20parishthiti%20nahi%20hain%20ki%20ye%20achanak%20kardena%20padhe.%20Dekho%2C%20kisi%2022%20December%20ki%20raat%20ko%20wahan%20murtiyan%20rakh%20di%20gayi%20thi.%20Wo%20ek%20paristhiti%20thi%E2%80%A6aur%20jis%20raat%20ko%20dhandcha%20hataya%20ja%20raha%20tha%2C%20tab%20koi%20muhurat%20thodi%20na%20dekha%20gaya%20tha%E2%80%A6kya%20tab%20kisi%20shankaracharya%20ne%20prashn%20uthaya.%20Nahi%2C%20kyuki%20tab%20paristhiti%20thi.%20(%3C%2Fem%3EIt%20is%20the%20duty%20of%20the%20Shankaracharyas%20to%20follow%20and%20enforce%20the%20shashtra%20vidhi.%20Now%20the%20shashtra%20vidhi%20is%20being%20ignored.%20The%20first%20thing%20to%20note%20is%20that%20the%20temple%20is%20not%20yet%20complete%2C%20and%20prayers%20are%20in%20progress.%20There%20is%20no%20such%20situation%20that%20this%20should%20be%20done%20suddenly.%20See%2C%20on%20the%20night%20of%2022nd%20December%2C%20an%20idol%20was%20placed%20there.%20That%20was%20a%20situation.%20That%20night%20when%20the%20strructure%20was%20being%20lifted%20%5Breferring%20to%20Babri%20Masjid%5D%2C%20then%20no%20Shankaracharya%20asked%20this%20question.%20Because%20it%20was%20a%20situation.)%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3E%E2%80%9CAb%20koi%20paristhiti%20nahi%20hain%20ki%2022%20tareek%20ko%20hi%20karna%20hain.%20Aaj%20humare%20paas%20mauka%20hain%2C%20hum%20ache%20se%20pratishta%20karke%20mana%20kar%20sakte%20hain.%20%3C%2Fem%3E(Ab%20koi%20paristhiti%20nahi%20hain%20ki%2022%20tareek%20ko%20hi%20karna%20hain.%20Aaj%20humare%20paas%20mauka%20hain%2C%20hum%20ache%20se%20pratishta%20karke%20mana%20kar%20sakte%20hain.)%3Cem%3E%E2%80%9C%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3E%E2%80%9CLekin%20phir%20bhi%20adhoore%20mandir%20mein%20pratishta%20kardi%20ja%20rahi%20hain.%20To%20ye%20hum%20kaise%20sweekaar%20karle.%3C%2Fem%3E%20(But%20still%20the%20incomplete%20temple%20is%20being%20consecrated.%20So