Cp%3E%E2%80%9CMy%20life%20revolved%20around%20dance.%20Now%2C%20I%20could%20no%20longer%20dance%20or%20pursue%20science.%20I%20felt%20depressed%20and%20wondered%20what%20would%20happen%20to%20my%20hopes%20and%20dreams%20when%20I%20couldn%E2%80%99t%20even%20walk%20three%20steps%20without%20wincing.%20I%20attempted%20suicide%20too%2C%E2%80%9D%20she%20says.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHer%20wake-up%20call%20came%20in%20the%20form%20of%20a%20visit%20to%20the%20Victoria%20Hospital%20to%20collect%20her%20physical%20disability%20certificate.%20Here%2C%20she%20met%20a%20lady%20who%20didn%E2%80%99t%20have%20both%20feet%20and%20had%20travelled%20to%20Bengaluru%20from%20Tumakuru%2C%20with%20an%20infant%20in%20tow.%20Veena%20watched%20in%20awe%20as%20that%20lady%20fed%20her%20baby%20and%20played%20with%20him.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CMy%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F330237%2Fnellayapan-b-kanniyakumari-osd-to-nagaland-chief-minister-inspiring-story-went-viral-on-twitter%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Etroubles%20felt%20inconsequential%20%3C%2Fa%3Ein%20front%20of%20hers.%20She%20was%20happy%20and%20even%20managed%20to%20cook.%20She%20got%20her%20baby%20from%20so%20far%20away%20and%20led%20a%20regular%20life.%20So%20I%20thought%20why%20couldn%E2%80%99t%20I%3F%20I%20too%20could%20and%20would%20do%20everything%20I%20ever%20wanted%2C%E2%80%9D%20she%20says.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBack%20home%20in%20January%202013%2C%20with%20hardly%20two%20months%20for%20the%20board%20exams%2C%20Veena%20started%20going%20for%20tuition%20classes%2C%20assisted%20by%20her%20father.%20She%20managed%20to%20pass%20the%20exams%20with%20a%20decent%20score.%20Since%20going%20to%20college%20in%20a%20city%20like%20Bengaluru%20would%20be%20difficult%2C%20she%20shifted%20to%20Puducherry%20to%20her%20grandmother%E2%80%99s%20place%20and%20pursued%20her%20degrees%20there.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAfter%20her%20post-graduation%2C%20she%20switched%20jobs%20from%20banks%20to%20IT%20but%20the%20stress%20of%20a%20desk%20job%20was%20too%20much%20to%20take.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CI%20had%20a%20project%20with%20a%20South%20American%20company%2C%20which%20meant%20office%20work%20from%209%20to%206%20followed%20by%20meetings%20at%209%3A30%20pm%20which%20often%20got%20over%20by%201%20to%202%20am.%20The%20stress%20on%20my%20leg%20led%20to%20infection%20and%20hospitalisation%20for%2015%20days.%20That%E2%80%99s%20when%20I%20decided%20to%20quit%20the%20job%20in%20February%202023%2C%E2%80%9D%20she%20says.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3EServing%20a%20taste%20of%20Tamil%20Nadu%20in%20Bengaluru%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cblockquote%20data-instgrm-version%3D%5C%2214%5C%22%20data-instgrm-permalink%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.instagram.com%2Freel%2FCuo5vKfgFLX%2F%3Futm_source%3Dig_embed%26amp%3Butm_campaign%3Dloading%5C%22%3E%3Cdiv%3E%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.instagram.com%2Freel%2FCuo5vKfgFLX%2F%3Futm_source%3Dig_embed%26utm_campaign%3Dloading%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3EView%20this%20post%20on%20Instagram%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cp%3E%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.instagram.com%2Freel%2FCuo5vKfgFLX%2F%3Futm_source%3Dig_embed%26utm_campaign%3Dloading%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EA%20post%20shared%20by%20Kari%20Dosa%20(%40karidosa_10)%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3C%2Fblockquote%3E%20%5Cn%3Cp%3EAfter%20quitting%2C%20Veena%20decided%20that%20she%20could%20follow%20her%20passion%20for%20food%20and%20open%20her%20own%20stall.%20Staying%20in%20Bengaluru%20since%20childhood%20and%20for%20work%2C%20she%20hadn%E2%80%99t%20found%20a%20single%20%3Cem%3Ekari%20dosa%20%3C%2Fem%3Eplace%2C%20which%20she%20craved.%20So%20when%20she%20thought%20of%20serving%20something%20that%20wasn%E2%80%99t%20easily%20available%20in%20Bengaluru%2C%20she%20thought%20of%20this.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EKari%20dosa%3C%2Fem%3E%2C%20traditionally%20made%20with%20mutton%20kheema%2C%20originated%20in%20Madurai%2C%20Tamil%20Nadu.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EShe%20worked%20on%20perfecting%20the%20recipes%20and%20tastes%20for%20two%20months%20before%20launching%20her%20food%20cart%20in%20J%20P%20Nagar%2C%20Bengaluru.%20Initially%2C%20her%20family%20wasn%E2%80%99t%20in%20favour%20of%20her%20starting%20this%20food%20enterprise%20that%20requires%20physical%20labour%20and%20standing%20for%20long%20periods%20of%20time%2C%20but%20she%20was%20resolute.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CI%20wanted%20to%20create%20my%20own%20brand%20and%20achieve%20something.%20I%20wanted%20to%20push%20my%20limits%20and%20do%20something%20new%20every%20day.%20If%20I%20could%20do%20a%20desk%20job%20for%20eight%20hours%20daily%2C%20why%20can%E2%80%99t%20I%20stand%20for%20four%20hours%3F%E2%80%9D%20she%20says.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EFrom%20a%20cushy%20job%20in%20an%20air-conditioned%20office%2C%20Veena%20now%20slogs%20it%20out%20on%20the%20streets%20of%20Bengaluru%2C%20in%20the%20hugely%20competitive%20street%20food%20market.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EShe%20starts%20her%20day%20at%204%3A30%20am%20every%20day%20and%20sells%20%3Cem%3Ekari%20dosas%3C%2Fem%3E%20made%20with%20chicken%3Cem%3E%20kheema%3C%2Fem%3E%2C%20prawn%20%3Cem%3Ethokku%20%3C%2Fem%3E(curry)%20and%20mutton%3Cem%3E%20kheema%3C%2Fem%3E.%20A%20plain%20%3Cem%3Edosa%3C%2Fem%3E%20is%20priced%20at%20Rs%2010%2C%20while%20the%20mutton%20%3Cem%3Ekari%20dosa%3C%2Fem%3E%20costs%20Rs%20150.%20The%20stall%20is%20open%20from%207%3A30%20am%20to%2011%3A30%20am.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EVeena%20managed%20to%20eventually%20convince%20her%20family.%20She%20says%20her%20husband%2C%20a%20fitness%20trainer%20by%20profession%2C%20is%20her%20biggest%20cheerleader.%20He%20helps%20her%20set%20up%20the%20cart%20daily%20while%20she%20manages%20all%20the%20shopping%2C%20cooking%20and%20serving%20herself.%20She%20faces%20a%20lot%20of%20challenges%20with%20standing%20for%20over%20four%20hours%20a%20day%2C%20but%20she%20pushes%20through%20as%20her%20mind%20is%20happy%2C%20she%20shares%20adding%20that%20she%20finds%20happiness%20in%20the%20satisfaction%20of%20her%20customers.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CPain%20is%20everything.%20You%20have%20to%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F326200%2Fecosoul-home-india-boston-sustainable-plastic-free-kitchenware-cutlery-sugarcane-palm%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Etolerate%20the%20pain%20%3C%2Fa%3Eand%20find%20ways%20to%20overcome%20it.%20Look%20at%20people%20who%20are%20in%20worse%20situations%20and%20thank%20your%20stars%20for%20your%20life.%20That%E2%80%99s%20how%20I%20look%20at%20it.%20We%20can%E2%80%99t%20achieve%20anything%20without%20going%20through%20a%20struggle.%20Life%20is%20about%20overcoming%20hurdles%2C%E2%80%9D%20she%20adds.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EVeena%20lives%20by%20the%20mantra%3A%20%E2%80%9CNo%20matter%20how%20hard%20life%20hits%20you%2C%20be%20stronger%20than%20before.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EYou%20can%20visit%20Veena%E2%80%99s%20stall%20at%20Cassia%20Block%2C%20JP%20Nagar%207th%20Phase%20and%20reach%20out%20to%20her%20%3C%2Fem%3E%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%20nofollow%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.instagram.com%2Fkaridosa_10%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%3Cem%3Ehere%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cem%3E.%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EEdited%20by%20Pranita%