n%20once%20it%20was%20ruled%20a%20suicide%2C%20they%20saw%20no%20reason%20to%20dig%20deeper.%20It%20seems%20like%20a%20cover%20up.%20Why%20can't%20I%20find%20his%20pre-hospital%20care%20report%20and%20why%20can't%20I%20get%20the%20911%20call%3F%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EEpstein%20was%20convicted%20in%20Florida%20in%202008%20of%20paying%20young%20girls%20for%20massages%20but%20served%20just%2013%20months%20in%20jail%20under%20a%20secret%20plea%20deal%20struck%20with%20the%20then%20state%20prosecutor.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHis%20name%20hit%20headlines%20again%20after%20a%20New%20York%20judge%20began%20to%20unseal%20the%20identities%20of%20people%20linked%20in%20court%20documents%20to%20Epstein.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20documents%2C%20which%20contain%20almost%201%2C000%20pages%20of%20depositions%20and%20statements%2C%20notably%20include%20former%20US%20presidents%20Bill%20Clinton%20and%20Donald%20Trump%2C%20who%20have%20not%20been%20accused%20of%20any%20wrongdoing%20in%20the%20case.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20Britain%2C%20police%20said%20last%20week%20there%20would%20be%20no%20investigation%20after%20Prince%20Andrew%20--%20accused%20in%20the%20documents%20of%20groping%20a%20woman%2C%20which%20he%20denies%20--%20was%20reported%20to%20police%20by%20an%20anti-monarchy%20group.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%202019%2C%20a%20forensic%20pathologist%20hired%20by%20Epstein's%20brother%20said%20that%20evidence%20suggested%20the%20disgraced%20financier%20had%20not%20died%20by%20suicide%20in%20his%20jail%20cell%20but%20had%20been%20murdered.%20Michael%20Baden%20contradicted%20the%20official%20verdict%20of%20suicide%20by%20hanging%20given%20by%20officials%20in%20August%2C%20saying%20Epstein's%20injuries%20were%20%26quot%3Bmore%20indicative%20of%20homicidal%20strangulation.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHe%20said%20multiple%20fractures%20found%20in%20Epstein's%20neck%20--%20specifically%20the%20hyoid%20bone%20and%20thyroid%20cartilage%20--%20were%20%26quot%3Bvery%20unusual%20for%20suicide