areer%20in%20showbiz.%20He%20wanted%20her%20to%20pursue%20higher%20education%20and%20sent%20her%20to%20Chandigarh%2C%20but%20Kangana%20chose%20a%20different%20path%20and%20expressed%20her%20desire%20to%20pursue%20theater%20in%20Bombay.%20Her%20father%2C%20unable%20to%20understand%20this%20unconventional%20choice%2C%20decided%20to%20no%20longer%20act%20as%20her%20guardian.%20However%2C%20Kangana's%20success%20in%20showbiz%20has%20now%20made%20her%20father%20proud.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fentertainment%2Fhindi%2Fbollywood%2Fnews%2Fkangana-ranaut-reveals-her-father-wanted-to-shoot-her-with-a-rifle-for-this-reason%2Farticleshow%2F106672185.cms%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22INDIA%20Bloc%20Seat%20Sharing%20Talks%20In%20Progress%20For%20Maharashtra%2C%20UP%20Next%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EThe%20Opposition%20INDIA%20bloc%20is%20moving%20fast%20with%20discussions%20on%20seat-sharing%2C%20scheduling%20meetings%20cheek-by-jowl%20in%20multiple%20states.%20After%20talks%20started%20on%20Delhi%20and%20Punjab%2C%20today%20is%20the%20turn%20of%20two%20of%20the%20country's%20largest%20states%20--%20Uttar%20Pradesh%20and%20Maharashtra%20--%20which%20account%20for%20128%20of%20the%20543%20Lok%20Sabha%20seats.%3Cbr%3E%5Cn%C2%A0%3Cbr%3E%5CnWhile%20a%20meeting%20is%20on%20way%20in%20Mumbai%20between%20the%20Shiv%20Sea%20UBT%2C%20Sharad%20Pawar's%20Nationalist%20Congress%20Party%20and%20the%20Congress%20in%20Maharashtra%2C%20one%20more%20is%20scheduled%20this%20evening%20to%20divide%20the%2080%20seats%20of%20Uttar%20Pradesh.That%20will%20be%20held%20at%206%20pm%20at%20the%20Delhi%20residence%20of%20senior%20party%20leader%20Mukul%20Wasnik.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ENot%20a%20single%20one%20of%20these%20negotiations%20are%20expected%20to%20be%20easy%20for%20the%20Congress.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWhile%20there%20is%20no%20love%20lost%20between%20the%20party%20and%20the%20Akhilesh%20Yadav's%20Samajwadi%20Party%20and%20Arvind%20Kejriwal's%20Aam%20Aadmi%20Party%2C%20talks%20with%20MVA%20(Maha%20Vikas%20Aghadi)%20allies%20in%20Maharashtra%20also%20are%20expected%20to%20come%20with%20its%20own%20set%20of%20challenges.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Shiv%20Sena%20UBT%20has%20made%20it%20clear%20that%20as%20the%20%26quot%3Bbiggest%20party%26quot%3B%20in%20the%20alliance%2C%20it%20expects%20no%20less%20than%2023%20seats.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThis%20is%20Maharashtra%2C%20and%20Shiv%20Sena%20is%20the%20biggest%20party%20here...%20We%20have%20always%20said%20that%20Shiv%20Sena%20has%20always%20been%20fighting%20on%2023%20seats%20in%20the%20Lok%20Sabha%20elections%20including%20Dadra%20and%20Nagar%20Haveli%20and%20that%20will%20be%20firm%2C%26quot%3B%20senior%20party%20leader%20Sanjay%20Raut%20had%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThis%20would%20leave%20exactly%2025%20seats%20to%20be%20divided%20between%20Sharad%20Pawar's%20Nationalist%20Congress%20Party%20and%20the%20Congress%2C%20which%20has%20got%20a%20limited%20say%2C%20given%20the%20minimum%20heft%20it%20has%20in%20the%20state.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20the%202019%20assembly%20elections%2C%20the%20Congress%20won%20only%2044%20seats%20in%20the%20288-member%20assembly%20--%20way%20lower%20than%20either%20of%20its%20allies.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20Uttar%20Pradesh%2C%20the%20Samajwadi%20Party%20is%20not%20expected%20to%20be%20in%20a%20forgiving%20mood%20given%20the%20state%20Congress's%20refusal%20to%20share%20any%20seats%20in%20the%20assembly%20elections.%20State%20party%20chief%20Kamal%20Nath%20had%20refused%20to%20honour%20the%20central%20leadership's%20commitment%20for%20six%20seats%20in%20the%20state.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20ripples%20were%20very%20public.%20Akhilesh%20Yadav's%20swipes%20at%20the%20Congress%20were%20followed%20by%20the%20party's%20crushing%20defeat%20in%20the%20three%20heartland%20states%20and%20the%20sacking%20of%20Kamal%20Nath%20from%20the%20top%20post.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20situation%20is%20further%20complicated%20by%20the%20Congress's%20poor%20performance%20in%20Uttar%20Pradesh.%20The%20Samajwadi%20Party%20considers%20it%20liability%20since%20the%20assembly%20polls%20of%202017%2C%20when%20the%20two%20parties%20contested%20as%20allies%20and%20got%20trounced.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Samajwadi%20Party%2C%20which%20was%20ruling%20the%20state%20since%202012%2C%20is%20yet%20to%20gain%20enough%20ground%20to%20defeat%20the%20Yogi%20Adityanath-led%20BJP%20government.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20SP%2C%20which%20got%20reduced%20to%2047%20seats%20in%202017%20from%20the%20224%20it%20had%2C%20recouped%20some%20of%20the%20seats%20last%20year.%20It%20won%20111%20seats%2C%20up%20by%2064.%20But%20the%20BJP%20was%20way%20ahead%20with%20255%20seats.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ECongress's%20discussion%20with%20AAP%20is%20also%20proving%20contentious.%20While%20the%20party%20wants%204%20seats%20in%20Delhi%20and%20seven%20seats%20in%20Punjab%2C%20AAP%20is%20not%20ready%20to%20comply.%20In%20both%20Delhi%20and%20Punjab%2C%20the%20ruling%20party%20wants%20the%20bigger%20share%20of%20seats.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20Bengal%2C%20Congress%20would%20like%20to%20have%20five%20seats.%20But%20Trinamool%20Congress%20chief%20and%20Chief%20Minister%20Mamata%20Banerjee%20has%20made%20it%20clear%20that%20she%20is%20not%20ready%20to%20offer%20any.%20The%20matter%20has%20not%20been%20officially%20discussed%20yet.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20Bihar%2C%20the%20Congress%20and%20the%20Rashtriya%20Janata%20Dal%20have%20conducted%20the%20preliminary%20talks.%20Nitish%20Kumar's%20Janata%20Dal%20United%20will%20not%20settle%20for%20less%20than%2017%20of%20the%20state's%2040%20seats.%20It%20is%20likely%20that%20the%20RJD%20would%20also%20contest%2017%20seats%20in%20line%20with%20the%202015%20assembly%20polls%20formula.%20Five%20seats%20can%20go%20to%20the%20Congress%20and%20one%20to%20the%20CPI-ML.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1704806400000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2019-11%2Fb6ogiprg_uddhav-sharad-pawar-and-kharge-show-of-strength-mumbai-pti-650_650x400_25_November_19.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Findia-bloc-seat-sharing-talks-in-progress-for-maharashtra-up-next-4830071%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22The%20Opposition%20INDIA%20bloc%20is%20moving%20fast%20with%20discussions%20on%20seat-sharing%2C%20scheduling%20meetings%20cheek-by-jowl%20in%20multiple%20states.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Findia-bloc-seat-sharing-talks-in-progress-for-maharashtra-up-next-4830071%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww-ndtv-com.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Findia-bloc-seat-sharing-talks-in-progress-for-maharashtra-up-next-4830071%2Famp%2F1%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Findia-bloc-seat-sharing-talks-in-progress-for-maharashtra-up-next-4830071%2Famp%2F1%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22PFC%20gets%20RBI%20nod%20to%20set%20up%20wholly-owned%20finance%20company%20in%20GIFT%20City%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1704806374000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fbsmedia.business-standard.com%2F_media%2Fbs%2Fimg%2Farticle%2F2019-07%2F07%2Ffull%2F1562516878-6264.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.business-standard.com%2Fcompanies%2Fnews%2Fpfc-gets-rbi-nod-to-set-up-wholly-owned-finance-company-in-gift-city-124010900933_1.html%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22The%20company%20is%20planning%20to%20set%20up%20a%20subsidiary%20at%20the%20International%20Financial%20Services%20Centre%20(IFSC)%20in%20GIFT%20City%2C%20Gujarat%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.business-standard.com%2Fcompanies%2Fnews%2Fpfc-gets-rbi-nod-to-set-up-wholly-owned-finance-company-in-gift-city-124010900933_1.html%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww-business--standard-com.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Fwww.business-standard.com%2Famp%2Fcompanies%2Fnews%2Fpfc-gets-rbi-nod-to-set-up-wholly-owned-finance-company-in-gift-city-124010900933_1.html%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.business-standard.com%2Famp%2Fcompanies%2Fnews%2Fpfc-gets-rbi-nod-to-set-up-wholly-owned-finance-company-in-gift-city-124010900933_1.html%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Vijayakanth's%20Political%20Journey%20Was%20a%20Blend%20of%20Aspiration%2C%20Courage%2C%20Mistakes%20and%20Harsh%20Realities%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cimg%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F01%2F09182944%2FVijayakanth.png%5C%22%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20recent%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fpolitics%2Fvijayakanth-no-more%5C%22%3Epassing%20of%20Vijayakanth%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20an%20eminent%20Tamil%20film%20star-turned-politician%2C%20marks%20the%20end%20of%20a%20significant%20albeit%20overlooked%20chapter%20in%20Tamil%20Nadu%E2%80%99s%20political%20narrative.%20His%20transition%20from%20the%20movie%20industry%20to%20the%20political%20arena%20was%20not%20just%20a%20career%20shift%2C%20but%20a%20transformative%20journey%20that%20redefined%20the%20contours%20of%20Tamil%20Nadu%E2%80%99s%20political%20and%20social%20landscape.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EVijayakanth%E2%80%99s%20film%20career%20laid%20the%20foundation%20for%20his%20political%20journey.%20As%20the%20elected%20president%20of%20the%20South%20Indian%20Artistes%E2%80%99%20Association%2C%20also%20known%20as%20the%20Nadigar%20Sangam%2C%20he%20demonstrated%20his%20ability%20to%20lead%20and%20mediate%20in%20an%20industry%20rife%20with%20socio-economic%20and%20political%20divisions.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHis%20work%20in%20the%20Nadigar%20Sangam%20in%20the%20late%201990s%20and%20early%202000s%20provides%20a%20valuable%20lens%20to%20understand%20the%20interplay%20of%20the%20Dravidian-Tamil%20ethos%20among%20the%20Tamil%20diaspora%20across%20the%20world.%20His%20popularity%20in%20cinema%20and%20his%20philanthropy%20did%20not%20just%20win%20him%20fans%2C%20but%20built%20an%20organisational%20base%20that%20later%20morphed%20into%20a%20political%20force.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHis%20media%20profile%20and%20portrayal%20of%20heroic%20characters%20resonated%20with%20the%20public%20at%20the%20time%2C%20crafting%20an%20image%20of%20a%20benevolent%20and%20approachable%20leader.%20Crucially%2C%20the%20financial%20success%20of%20his%20film%20career%20provided%20the%20resources%20necessary%20to%20fuel%20his%20political%20ambitions.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3E%E2%80%98%3Cem%3EKaruppu%3C%2Fem%3E%20MGR%E2%80%99%20and%20the%20politics%20of%20subversion%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EVijayakanth%E2%80%99s%20film%20persona%2C%20reminiscent%20of%20M.G.%20Ramachandran%20(MGR)%E2%80%99s%20style%2C%20helped%20him%20appeal%20to%20a%20wide%20electorate.%20His%20leadership%20in%20the%202006%20assembly%20elections%20and%20the%202009%20Lok%20Sabha%20elections%20established%20his%20Desiya%20Murpokku%20Dravida%20Kazhagam%20(DMDK)%20party%20as%20a%20notable%20force%20in%20Tamil%20Nadu%E2%80%99s%20politics.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EVijayakanth%E2%80%99s%20approach%20to%20politics%20was%20marked%20by%20an%20astute%20use%20of%20populism.%20Though%20he%20was%20popularly%20referred%20to%20as%20%E2%80%98%3Cem%3EKaruppu%20%3C%2Fem%3EMGR%E2%80%99%20(dark-skinned%20MGR)%20due%20to%20the%20similarities%20in%20their%20persona%20and%20of%20their%20screen%20titles%2C%20Vijayakanth%E2%80%99s%20style%20of%20politics%20was%20in%20effect%20a%20subversion%20of%20MGR%E2%80%99s%20style%20of%20politics.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cins%3EAlso%20read%20%7C%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fpolitics%2Fbjp-trojan-horse-left-winger-vagueness-at-the-heart-of-kamal-haasans-politics%5C%22%3E%E2%80%98BJP%20Trojan%20Horse%E2%80%99%2C%20%E2%80%98Left%20Winger%E2%80%99%3A%20Vagueness%20at%20the%20Heart%20of%20Kamal%20Haasan%E2%80%99s%20Politics%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fins%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAs%20observed%20by%20Dr%20Andrew%20Wyatt%2C%20Vijayakanth%E2%80%99s%20political%20strategy%20mirrored%20the%20%E2%80%98protectionist%E2%80%99%20populism%20of%20MGR%2C%20i.e.%20the%20amalgamation%20of%20diverse%20social%20groups%20rather%20than%20catering%20to%20specific%20caste%2C%20regional%20or%20sub-regional%20interests.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHowever%2C%20unlike%20MGR%2C%20Vijayakanth%20neither%20sought%20nor%20secured%20the%20definitive%20support%20of%20numerically%20dominant%20caste%20groups.%20Instead%2C%20he%20built%20a%20broad%20coalition%20of%20support%20by%20voicing%20his%20opposition%20to%20caste-based%20parties%20and%20focusing%20on%20the%20needs%20of%20the%20marginalised.%20Such%20an%20approach%20sought%20to%20unsettle%20the%20sub-regional%20geographic%20dominance%20exerted%20by%20a%20few%20numerically%20dominant%20caste%20groups.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHis%20outreach%20to%20women%20and%20the%20symbolic%20use%20of%20the%20%3Cem%3Emurasu%3C%2Fem%3E%20(drum)%2C%20an%20emblem%20of%20the%20marginalised%20(Dalits)%2C%20in%20his%20party%E2%80%99s%20imagery%2C%20demonstrated%20an%20astute%20understanding%20of%20social%20dynamics%20in%20Tamil%20Nadu%20and%20of%20the%20Dravidian-Tamil%20ethos.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThis%20approach%20set%20him%20up%20to%20transcend%20traditional%20caste%20and%20class%20barriers%20in%20gaining%20support%20from%20diverse%20groups%20across%20the%20state%2C%20bringing%20his%20style%20of%20politics%20closer%20to%20the%20DMK%20and%20Karunanidhi%20in%20particular.%20This%20explains%20his%20party%E2%80%99s%20considerable%20vote%20shares%20in%20the%202006%20and%202009%20elections%2C%20which%20translated%20into%20seats%20when%20in%20alliance%20with%20a%20Dravidian%20major%2C%20the%20AIADMK%2C%20in%202011.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EDMDK%E2%80%99s%20short-lived%20success%20and%20the%20Dravidian%20majors%E2%80%99%20resilience%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EDr%20Wyatt%20noted%20that%20the%20DMDK%20grappled%20with%20maintaining%20institutional%20pluralism.%20The%20centralisation%20of%20power%20around%20Vijayakanth%E2%80%99s%20persona%20and%20the%20uncertain%20tolerance%20for%20diverse%20opinions%20within%20the%20party%20raised%20questions%20about%20its%20long-term%20institutional%20health.%20A%20case%20in%20point%20is%20his%20refusal%20to%20cater%20to%20his%20party-wide%20request%20to%20form%20an%20alliance%20with%20the%20DMK%20ahead%20of%20the%202016%20elections.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20other%20words%2C%20while%20his%20outreach%20strategy%20was%20congruent%20with%20Karunanidhi%E2%80%99s%2C%20he%20could%20not%20be%20the%20conciliator-in-chief%20within%20the%20party.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAlso%2C%20his%20stardom%20and%20hold%20over%20the%20party%20and%20its%20members%20were%20not%20comparable%20to%20that%20of%20MGR.%20As%20a%20result%2C%20he%20could%20not%20prevent%20defections%20and%20could%20not%20find%20replacements%20for%20such%20defectors%20in%20the%20corresponding%20constituencies.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cins%3EAlso%20read%3A%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fpolitics%2Frajinikanth-tamil-nadu-politics-vijayakanth-dmdk%5C%22%3EIn%20the%20Rise%20and%20Fall%20of%20Vijayakanth%20in%20Tamil%20Politics%2C%20Rajinikanth%20Has%20a%20Lesson%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fins%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHis%20deteriorating%20health%20and%20the%20emergence%20of%20his%20family%20members%20at%20the%20helm%20who%20could%20not%20fill%20his%20shoes%2C%20and%20more%20importantly%2C%20tomfoolery%20vis-%C3%A0-vis%20alliance%20decisions%2C%20enfeebled%20the%20party%20and%20its%20electoral%20prospects%20further.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20effect%2C%20the%20DMDK%20lost%20ideological%20coherence%20and%20a%20stable%20connect%20with%20the%20people.%20The%20Dravidian%20majors%20on%20the%20other%20hand%2C%20after%20a%20few%20initial%20setbacks%2C%20were%20able%20to%20regain%20their%20electoral%20dominance%20and%2C%20in%20the%20process%2C%20saw%20more%20members%20of%20the%20DMDK%20join%20them.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EFurthermore%2C%20despite%20effectuating%20substantive%20impact%2C%20he%20did%20not%20draw%20the%20attention%20of%20the%20political%20discourse%20and%20opinion%20makers%20akin%20to%20that%20of%20his%20fellow%20actors%20like%20Rajinikanth%20or%20Kamal%20Haasan%2C%20who%20drew%20a%20lot%20of%20attention%20even%20over%20non-committal%20signalling.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThis%20could%20be%20attributed%20to%20Vijayakanth%E2%80%99s%20last%20few%20movies%20that%20neither%20succeeded%20financially%20nor%20resonated%20with%20audiences%2C%20as%20well%20as%20to%20a%20weaker%20connect%20with%20his%20fans%20since%20he%20started%20his%20political%20party.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAt%20the%20same%20time%2C%20he%20failed%20to%20proactively%20create%20a%20communication%20ecosystem%20to%20reach%20out%20to%20the%20public%20and%20the%20discourse-makers%3B%20worse%2C%20when%20he%20got%20his%20opportunities%2C%20he%20damaged%20his%20reputation%20by%20losing%20his%20composure%20on%20camera%20and%20in%20public%20many%20a%20time.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EAdieu%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EVijayakanth%E2%80%99s%20political%20endeavours%2C%20while%20short-lived%2C%20created%20significant%20ripples%20in%20Tamil%20Nadu%E2%80%99s%20electoral%20politics.%20His%20efforts%20illuminate%20the%20electoral%20arena%E2%80%99s%20receptiveness%20to%20charismatic%20leaders%20while%20also%20underscoring%20the%20importance%20of%20building%20robust%20party%20structures.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20retrospect%2C%20Vijayakanth%E2%80%99s%20political%20journey%20was%20a%20blend%20of%20aspiration%2C%20courage%2C%20mistakes%20and%20the%20harsh%20realities%20of%20Tamil%20Nadu%E2%80%99s%20political%20arena.%20As%20we%20bid%20farewell%20to%20Vijayakanth%2C%20it%20is%20crucial%20to%20acknowledge%20his%20unique%20contribution%20to%20Tamil%20Nadu%E2%80%99s%20political%20narrative.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHis%20story%20is%20not%20just%20about%20the%20transient%20impact%20of%20a%20celebrity%20in%20politics%2C%20but%20also%20about%20the%20broader%20dynamics%20of%20power%2C%20culture%20and%20populism%20in%20one%20of%20India%E2%80%99s%20most%20politically%20vibrant%20states.%20His%20legacy%2C%20as%20a%20symbol%20of%20the%20potential%20and%20limitations%20of%20star%20power%20in%20politics%2C%20will%20continue%20to%20be%20a%20subject%20of%20interest%20and%20analysis%20for%20years%20to%20come.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fauthor%2Fvignesh-karthik-kr%5C%22%3EVignesh%20Karthik%20K.R.%3C%2Fa%3E%20is%20a%20Postdoctoral%20Research%20Fellow%20of%20Indian%20and%20Indonesian%20Politics%20at%20the%20Royal%20Netherlands%20Institute%20of%20Southeast%20Asian%20and%20Caribbean%20Studies.%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1704806146000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F01%2F09182944%2FVijayakanth.png%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fpolitics%2Fvijayakanth-an-apparent-enigma-in-tamil-nadus-politics%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22The%20recently%20passed%20film%20star-turned-politician's%20efforts%20illuminate%20the%20electoral%20arena's%20receptiveness%20to%20charismatic%20leaders%20while%20also%20underscoring%20the%20importance%20of%20building%20robust%20party%20structures.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A3%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fpolitics%2Fvijayakanth-an-apparent-enigma-in-tamil-nadus-politics%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Bandhan%20Bank%20clarifies%20the%20NCGTC%20audit%20is%20only%20on%20CGFMU%20loan%20claims%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1704805852000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fbsmedia.business-standard.com%2F_media%2Fbs%2Fimg%2Farticle%2F2022-04%2F13%2Ffull%2F1649867811-1983.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.business-standard.com%2Fcompanies%2Fnews%2Fbandhan-bank-clarifies-the-ncgtc-audit-is-only-on-cgfmu-loan-claims-124010900936_1.html%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22CGFMU%20is%20a%20government-established%20trust%20fund%20which%20ensures%20payment%20