wer%20in%20Telangana%20in%202023%20after%20almost%20a%20decade%20of%20struggle.%20Almost%20the%20entire%20Congress%20unit%20shifted%20to%20the%20YSR%20Congress%20formed%20by%20Rajasekhara%20Reddy%E2%80%99s%20son%20Jagan%20Mohan%20Reddy%2C%20who%20registered%20one%20of%20the%20biggest%20victories%20in%20the%202019%20assembly%20elections%20against%20its%20principal%20rival%20Telugu%20Desam%20Party%20led%20by%20N.%20Chandrababu%20Naidu.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAmidst%20all%20the%20political%20churn%2C%20the%20BJP%2C%20too%2C%20has%20remained%20unsuccessful%20in%20making%20inroads%20in%20the%20state.%20It%20has%20attempted%20to%20poach%20influential%20leaders%20from%20both%20the%20TDP%20and%20YSR%20Congress%2C%20pressed%20both%20the%20regional%20parties%20to%20toe%20its%20political%20line%20in%20the%20Parliament%20by%20keeping%20federal%20funds%20tightly%20under%20its%20control%2C%20and%20kept%20the%20Sword%20of%20Damocles%20hanging%20over%20both%20Jagan%20and%20Naidu%E2%80%99s%20heads%20through%20central%20investigation%20agencies.%20The%20carrot%20and%20stick%20approach%20adopted%20by%20the%20Narendra%20Modi-led%20BJP%20towards%20both%20the%20YSR%20Congress%20and%20TDP%2C%20however%2C%20has%20alienated%20the%20saffron%20party%20further%20in%20the%20state.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBoth%20regional%20parties%20have%20taken%20a%20special%20dislike%20towards%20the%20BJP%20for%20its%20alleged%20blackmailing%20tactics%20and%20are%20willing%20to%20work%20with%20the%20Centre%20only%20for%20convenience%20instead%20of%20any%20true%20ideological%20reasons.%20The%20tricky%2C%20multi-layered%20politics%20that%20is%20currently%20unfolding%20in%20Andhra%20Pradesh%2C%20set%20to%20witness%20another%20round%20of%20simultaneous%20assembly%20and%20Lok%20Sabha%20polls%20in%202024%2C%20is%20a%20case%20in%20point.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fpolitics%2Finterview-telugu-desam-party-nara-lokesh-jaganmohan%5C%22%3ETDP%20scion%20Nara%20Lokesh%20in%20a%20recent%20interview%20to%20%3Cem%3EThe%3C%2Fem%3E%20%3Cem%3EWire%3C%2Fem%3E%20said%20that%20it%20has%20adopted%20an%20%E2%80%9Cequidistant%20policy%3C%2Fa%3E%E2%80%9D%20towards%20both%20the%20Congress%20and%20the%20BJP.%20Given%20that%20the%20TDP%20has%20historically%20been%20an%20anti-Congress%20platform%20and%20has%20been%20a%20part%20of%20the%20BJP-led%20NDA%20earlier%2C%20the%20new%20posturing%20is%20significant.%20Lokesh%20denied%20all%20reports%20that%20spoke%20about%20a%20possible%20TDP-BJP%20alliance%20in%20the%20near%20future.%20The%20party%E2%80%99s%20campaign%20is%20focussed%20on%20Jagan%E2%80%99s%20alleged%20%E2%80%9Cautocratic%E2%80%9D%20regime%20that%2C%20according%20to%20Lokesh%2C%20has%20resulted%20in%20an%20all-round%20disenfranchisement%20of%20democratic%20institutions%20in%20the%20state%20%E2%80%93%20from%20Panchayats%20to%20Vidhan%20Sabha.%20%E2%80%9COver-centralisation%E2%80%9D%20of%20governance%20during%20Jagan%E2%80%99s%20rule%2C%20Lokesh%20said%2C%20has%20led%20to%20corrupt%20and%20crony%20practices%20in%20the%20state.%20The%20party%20has%20also%20attacked%20Jagan%20for%20supporting%20many%20of%20the%20Centre%E2%80%99s%20controversial%20bills%20in%20the%20Parliament.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ETDP%E2%80%99s%20line%20of%20canvassing%20bears%20stark%20resemblance%20to%20the%20larger%20opposition%E2%80%99s%20campaign%20against%20the%20Modi%20government.%20Most%20TDP%20leaders%20will%20privately%20tell%20you%20that%20the%20Jagan%20government%20is%20no%20different%20from%20the%20Modi%20government%20in%20the%20way%20it%20functions.%20Yet%2C%20TDP%20has%20not%20taken%20an%20open%20stance%20against%20the%20Centre%2C%20something%20that%20it%20did%20when%20N.%20Chandrababu%20Naidu%20walked%20out%20of%20the%20National%20Democratic%20Alliance%20(NDA)%20in%202018.%20It%20has%20allied%20with%20the%20Pawan%20Kalyan-led%20Jana%20Sena%2C%20which%20is%20a%20part%20of%20the%20NDA%20in%20Telangana.%20Lokesh%20said%20that%20Jana%20Sena%20is%20a%20BJP%20ally%20only%20in%20Telangana%20but%20not%20in%20Andhra%20Pradesh%2C%20as%20he%20asserted%20his%20party%E2%80%99s%20%E2%80%9Cequidistant%E2%80%9D%20policy%20from%20both%20the%20Congress%20and%20the%20BJP.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EObservers%20in%20the%20state%20believe%20that%20any%20hope%20of%20an%20alliance%20between%20the%20TDP%20and%20the%20BJP%20were%20dashed%20by%20Jagan%20when%20his%20government%20arrested%20Naidu%20in%20a%20corruption%20case%2C%20making%20it%20difficult%20for%20the%20saffron%20party%20to%20officially%20ally%20with%20the%20TDP.%20Given%20the%20BJP%E2%80%99s%20anti-corruption%20rhetoric%2C%20Jagan%20practically%20checkmated%20both%20its%20principal%20rival%20TDP%20and%20the%20BJP%2C%20while%20sending%20a%20strong%20message%20to%20the%20Centre%20to%20let%20both%20the%20regional%20parties%20fight%20it%20out%20on%20their%20own%20in%20the%20upcoming%20elections.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EJagan%2C%20however%2C%20is%20beset%20with%20his%20own%20problems.%20In%202019%2C%20he%20consolidated%20a%20majority%20of%20minority%20and%20Dalit%20votes%20in%20his%20favour.%20He%20has%20pursued%20a%20strong%20secular%20political%20line%20in%20the%20last%20five%20years%2C%20while%20also%20delivering%20a%20slew%20of%20welfare%20measures%20to%20the%20poor.%20However%2C%20his%20support%20to%20the%20Union%20government%E2%80%99s%20controversial%20bills%20in%20Parliament%20may%20have%20also%20driven%20away%20a%20substantial%20section%20of%20his%20supporters%2C%20especially%20those%20who%20have%20been%20traditional%20Congress%20workers%2C%20from%20his%20party.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAhead%20of%20the%202024%20elections%2C%20he%20is%20struggling%20to%20keep%20his%20house%20in%20order.%20His%20sister%20YS%20Sharmila%2C%20who%20was%20sidelined%20in%20the%20party%2C%20recently%20joined%20the%20Congress%20and%20is%20touted%20to%20play%20a%20prominent%20role%20in%20Andhra%20politics%20in%20the%20days%20to%20come.%20Her%20last-minute%20decision%20to%20withdraw%20from%20the%20recent%20electoral%20race%20played%20an%20important%20role%20in%20Congress%E2%80%99s%20victory%20in%20Telangana%20assembly%20elections.%20At%20the%20same%20time%2C%20many%20of%20his%20MLAs%20are%20facing%20strong%20anti-incumbency%20on%20the%20ground%2C%20forcing%20Jagan%20to%20announce%20many%20new%20faces%20as%20his%20party%E2%80%99s%20candidates.%20Moreover%2C%20his%20welfarist%20measures%20for%20the%20poor%20have%20alienated%20a%20large%20chunk%20of%20middle%20class%20voters.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHow%20much%20his%20own%20popularity%20among%20the%20poor%20counts%20in%20the%20upcoming%20assembly%20elections%20in%20the%20face%20of%20such%20hurdles%20remains%20to%20be%20seen%2C%20as%20a%20class%20divide%20among%20the%20voters%20is%20increasingly%20becoming%20more%20and%20more%20palpable.%20Naidu%2C%20on%20the%20other%20hand%2C%20has%20shown%20his%20ability%20to%20resuscitate%20after%20a%20string%20of%20failures.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Telugu%20parties%20remain%20malleable%20enough%20to%20move%20towards%20both%20UPA%20and%20NDA.%20Ahead%20of%20the%202024%20Lok%20Sabha%20polls%2C%20the%20BJP%2C%20which%20tried%20hard%20to%20gain%20a%20foothold%20in%20Andhra%20Pradesh%2C%20seems%20to%20have%20resigned%20to%20the%20fact%20that%20it%20has%20no%20hope%20of%20any%20electoral%20gain%20in%20the%20coastal%20state.%20It%20will%20mostly%20rely%20on%20its%20alleged%20pressure%20tactics%20to%20sway%20one%20of%20the%20regional%20parties%20in%20the%20case%20of%20a%20complicated%20post-poll%20scenario.%20Regional%20concerns%20and%20state%E2%80%99s%20autonomy%20will%20dictate%20political%20decisions%20made%20by%20both%20the%20TDP%20and%20YSR%20Congress.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20contrast%2C%20the%20Congress%20has%20laid%20the%20foundation%20stone%20for%20its%20revival%20in%20Andhra%20Pradesh%20by%20inducting%20Y.S.%20Sharmila.%20However%2C%20its%20way%20forward%20currently%20seems%20to%20be%20a%20long-winding%20and%20laborious%20one.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EThis%20piece%20was%20first%20published%20on%20The%20India%20Cab