y%20dad%E2%80%99s%20colleagues%20and%20asked%20who%20he%20was.%20Labelled%20as%20wrongdoers%2C%20they%20were%20being%20taken%20to%20the%20courtroom%20to%20face%20the%20consequences.%20I%20stood%20there%2C%20observing%20them%2C%20while%20their%20family%20members%20rushed%20towards%20them%2C%20engaging%20in%20fervent%20conversations%2C%E2%80%9D%20she%20adds.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ELooking%20at%20the%20family%20members%E2%80%99%20suffering%2C%20little%20Chaitali%20felt%20like%20she%20should%20do%20something%20for%20them.%20%E2%80%9CI%20was%20too%20young%20but%20I%20had%20made%20up%20my%20mind%20that%20I%20want%20to%20do%20something%20for%20them%2C%E2%80%9D%20she%20says.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAt%20this%20age%2C%20Chaitali%20decided%20she%20wanted%20to%20be%20a%20social%20worker%20and%20chose%20the%20path%20of%20helping%20others.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3ETaking%20Jute%20To%20the%20Global%20Stage%C2%A0%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%202015%2C%20after%20several%20years%20of%20working%20with%20various%20NGOs%2C%20Chaitali%20laid%20the%20foundation%20for%20the%20Rakshak%20Foundation.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20foundation%20focuses%20on%20empowering%20male%20and%20female%20inmates%20and%20other%20underprivileged%20women.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CI%20began%20my%20work%20at%20the%20correctional%20home%2C%20initially%20focusing%20on%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F247834%2Ftechnology-teacher-training-madhya-pradesh-government-schools-english-classes%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Espoken%20English%3C%2Fa%3E.%20Over%20time%2C%20I%E2%80%99ve%20undertaken%20various%20projects%2C%20including%20activities%20such%20as%20cookie-making%20with%20women%20and%20inmates%2C%20introducing%20yoga%20(especially%20during%20the%20COVID-19%20pandemic)%2C%20engaging%20in%20woodwork%2C%20and%20conducting%20painting%20sessions.%20The%20array%20of%20projects%20reflects%20the%20di