0with%20the%20National%20Jute%20Board%20of%20India%20(NJB).%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CThe%20training%20program%20spans%2045%20days%2C%20and%20we%20are%20proud%20to%20have%20partnered%20with%20NJB%20for%20its%20successful%20implementation.%20Our%20initial%20accomplishment%20was%20the%20training%20conducted%20at%20the%20Dandam%20Central%20Correctional%20Home%2C%20benefiting%20the%20prisoners%20there.%20Subsequently%2C%20I%20extended%20the%20initiative%20by%20providing%20additional%20training%2C%20leading%20to%20continued%20production%20and%20participation%20in%20various%20exhibitions%2C%E2%80%9D%20she%20says.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ETo%20promote%20acceptance%20and%20usage%2C%20the%20organisation%20implemented%20a%20practice%20of%20free%20gifting%20initially.%20This%20strategy%20aims%20to%20introduce%20people%20to%20the%20products%2C%20fostering%20acceptance%20and%20encouraging%20reuse%20in%20the%20long%20run.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CUnder%20this%20project%2C%20we%20have%20trained%20about%203%2C000%20inmates%20in%20making%20jute%20products.%20This%20project%20has%20evolved%20into%20%E2%80%98Root%20to%20Jute%E2%80%99.%20Notably%2C%20it%20has%20been%20incubated%20by%20the%20Indian%20Institute%20of%20Management%2C%E2%80%9D%20she%20informs.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ETrained%20and%20experienced%2C%20some%20of%20the%20inmates%20who%20have%20served%20their%20terms%20are%20even%20employed%20at%20Chaitali%E2%80%99s%20startup%2C%20becoming%20part%20of%20their%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F52355%2Fempowering-farmers-greenagtech%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Esupply%20chain%3C%2Fa%3E%20management%20teams.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20startup%20produces%20jute%20products%20such%20as%20handicrafts%2C%20rugs%2C%20and%20handbags.%20Additionally%2C%20she%20and%20her%20foundation%20created%20the%20Guinness%20World%20Record%20for%20creating%20the%20largest%20jute%20bag%20in%20the%20world%20on%20January%207%2C%2